hadiths[325]{hadithnumber,text}:
1,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi neend sey bedaar ho to apna haath wuzu key pani mein na daley yahan tak ke usey teen dafa dho ley kyonkey tum mein sey koi nahin janta ke uskey haath ney raat kahan guzari hai. (raat bhar kahan kahan lagta raha hai.)"
2,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) raat ko neend sey uthtey, to apney munh mubarak ko miswak key zariey sey saaf farmatey."
3,Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke main Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas gaya to aap daant saaf farma rahey they aur miswak ka sira aap ki zaban mubarak par tha aur aap (Aa-Aa) kar rahey they.
4,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya, jab ke merey sath do Ash-ari aur bhi they. eik merey daeyn tha aur doosra merey baeyn. aur Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) miswak farma rahey they. un dono ney aap sey koi ohda manga. mainey kaha : qism us zaat ki jisney aap ko sacha Nabi bana kar bheja ! unhoney mujhey apney dili iraday sey muttala nahin kya aur na mujhey andaza hi tha ke ye koi ohda mangengey. mujhey yun lagta hai ke main ab bhi dekh raha hun ke aap ki miswak aap key hont mubarak key nichey hai aur hont sikuda huwa hai. aap ney farmaya : tehqiq hum sarkari mansab par kisi aisey shakhs ka taawun hasil nahin kartey (ya hergiz nahin kerengey) jo us ka talabgar ho, lekin (aey Abu-Musa ! ) to (ohdey par) ja. phir aap ney unhein ( Abu-Musa ko haakim bana kar) Yamen bhej diya. phir aap ney unkey peechey Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi bhej diya."
5,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : miswak munh ki safai o pakizgi aur rab taala ki raza mandi ka zaria hai."
6,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tehqiq mainey miswak key barey mein tumhein bahut takeed ki hai."
7,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar ye baat na hoti ke main apni ummat par mashaqqat dal dunga, to main unhein har namaz key waqt miswak karney ka hukm deta."
8,"Qazi Shureh sey riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke mainey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey puchha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab ghar mein dakhil hotey to sab sey pehley kon sa kaam kartey they? unhoney farmaya : miswak kartey."
9,"Hazrat abu Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah ney farmaya : paanch cheezen fitri hain : khatna karana, zere-naf key baal mundna, munchhein kaatna, nakhun tarashna aur baghlon key baal ukhedna."
10,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch cheezen fitri hain, munchhon ko kaatna, baghlon key baal ukhedna, nakhun tarashna, zere-naf key baal saaf karna aur khatna karana."
11,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch cheezen fitrat sey hain : khatna karana, zere-naf key baal mundna, baghlon key baal ukhedna, nakhun kaatna aur munchhein tarashna."
12,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nakhun tarashna, munchhein kaatna aur zere-naf key baal mundna fitrat (ka taqaza) hai."
13,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apni munchhein na kaatey wo hum mein sey nahin."
14,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney munchhein kaatney, nakhun tarashney, zere-naf key baal moondney aur baghlon key baal ukhedney key liye ye muddat muqarrar ki hai ke hum chaalis din sey zayed na guzarney den. aur eik dafa rawi ney chaalis raat kaha."
15,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : munchhein khub mundao aur dadhi badhao."
16,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abu-Qirdad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : main Rasulullah key sath maidan mein gaya aur aap jab qazaey hajat ka irada farmatey to door jatey."
17,Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab qazaey hajat key liye jatey to door jatey. unhoney kaha : eik dafa aap eik safar mein they ke qazaey hajat key liye gaey to mujh sey farmaya : merey paas wuzu key liye pani laao. main pani laya to aap ney wuzu farmaya aur mozon par masah kya. Shekh ibne-Sunni (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney farmaya : (sanad mein mazkur raawi) Ismail sey murad (Ismail al-Qari) ibne-Jafar bin abu-Kasir hain.
18,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : main Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath chal raha tha ke aap eik qom key kudey karkat key dher key paas pahunchey to aap ney khadey khadey peshab kya. (aap key peshab karney sey pehley) main eik taraf hata to aap ney mujhey bulaya. main aap ki ediyon key paas (dusri taraf munh kar key) khada raha yahan tak ke aap farigh ho gaey. phir aap ney wuzu farmaya aur apney mozon par masah kya."
19,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab baitul-khala mein dakhil hotey, to farmatey : اللھم ! انی اعوذبک من الخبث و الخبائثaey Allah! main shararti Jinnon aur Jinniyon sey teri panah mein aata hun."
20,Raafey bin Is-haq sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat abu-Ayyub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ko shehar Misr mein ye kehtey suna : Allah ki qism ! main nahin janta ke un baitul-khalaon ko kya karun (jo ke qibley rukh baney huye hain) halanke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : jab tum mein sey koi bol o baraz (peshab pakhaney) key liye jaey to qibley ki taraf munh karey na peeth.
21,"Hazrat abu-Ayyub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bol o baraz key waqt qibley ki taraf munh karo na peeth balke mashriq ya maghrib ki taraf karo."
22,"Hazrat abu-Ayyub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi qazaey hajat karey to qibley ki taraf munh na karey balke mashriq ya maghrib ki taraf munh kerey. ( b-sharte-ke qibla mashriq ya maghrib ki taraf na ho)."
23,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : main apney ghar ki chhat par chadha to mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko do kachchi inton par baitul-maqdis ki taraf munh kiye huye qazaey hajat kartey dekha."
24,"Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi peshab karey to apney uzue-tanasul ( sharmgah ) ko daeyn haath sey na pakdey."
25,"Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi baitul-khala mein dakhil ho to apney uzue-tanasul ko daayan haath na lagaey."
26,Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik qom key kudey-karkat key dher par aaye aur wahan khadey khadey peshab kya.
27,Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik qom key kudey-karkat key dher par aaye aur wahan khadey khadey peshab kya.
28,Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik qom key kudey-karkat key dher ki taraf chaley phir khadey khadey peshab kya. Hadees key raawi Suleman (Alaihissalam) ney apni riwayat mein kaha : aur aap ney apney mozon par masah kya. jab ke ( unkey sathi ) mansoor ney masah ka zikr nahin kya.
29,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke jo shakhs tum sey bayan karey ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khadey ho kar peshab kya to uski tasdeeq na karo. aap beth kar hi peshab kartey they.
30,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Hasna (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye jab ke aap key haath mein dhaal jaisi koi chiz thi. aap ney usey nichey rakha aur uski ot mein beth kar peshab kya. logon mein sey eik shakhs kehney laga : dekho ! aap is tarah peshab kar rahey hain jaisey aurat peshab karti hai. aap ney uski baat sun li aur farmaya : kya tujhey ilm nahin ke Bani-Israel key eik shakhs ko kya saza mili thi ? unhein jab peshab lag jata to wo qainchi sey ( itna kapda ) kaat'tey they, chunanche unkey sathi ney unhein roka to usey qabr mein azab diya gaya."
31,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) do qabron key paas sey guzrey, to farmaya : tehqiq un qabron walon ko azab ho raha hai aur unhein kisi bhari kaam (ke jis sey bachna na-mumkin ho) ki wajeh sey azab nahin ho raha. is qabr wala to apney peshab key chhinton sey nahin bachta tha aur us qabr wala chughliyan khata tha. phir aap ney khajoor ki taza shakh mangwai aur usey cheer kar do hissey kar diya. phir eik us qabr par gaad di aur eik dusri par. phir farmaya : ummid hai jab tak ye khushk nahin hotin un sey azab mein takhfeef ki jaeygi. is riwayat ko bayan kartey huye mansoor ney aamash ki mukhalifat ki hai ke us ney ye riwayat Mujahid b-wasta ibne-Abbas bayan ki hai, yani Mujahid aur ibne-Abbas key darmiyan mein Taus ka wasta zikr nahin kya."
32,Hazrat Umaima binte-Ruqeqa (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas lakdi ka eik piyala tha jis mein aap (raat key waqt ) peshab kartey they. aur usey apni charpai key nichey rakh letey they.
33,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain : log kehtey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Ali ko wasiyat ki. haqiqat ye hai ke aap ney thal mangwaya ke is mein peshab keren, magar (us sey qabl hi) aap ka jism dhila pad gaya. (aap faut ho gaey ) mujhey pata bhi na chala, to aap ney kis ko wasiyat ki? Shekh ibn Sunni ney kaha, sanad mein mazkur raawi Azhar sey murad Azhar bin Sad Saman (ghi bechneywaley) hain."
34,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Sarjis (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs bal ( zamini surakh ) main peshab na kerey. shagirdon ney Qatada sey puchha ke bil mein peshab karna kyon mana hai? to unhoney kaha : kaha jata hai ke surakh jinnon ki rihaaish gaahen hain."
35,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney thehrey huye pani mein peshab karney sey mana farmaya hai.
36,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi apney ghusl ki jagah mein peshab na karey kyonkey umuman waswasey usi sey paida hotey hain."
37,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas sey guzra jab ke aap peshab kar rahey they, chunanche us ney aap ko salam kaha, magar aap ney usey salam ka jawab nahin diya."
38,"Hazrat muhaajir bin Qanfaz (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko salam kaha jab ke aap peshab kar rahey they, to aap ney salam ka jawab na diya yahan tak ke wuzu karney lagey aur jab wuzu mukammal kya to salam ka jawab diya."
39,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mana farmaya ke koi shakhs haddi ya leed sey safai kerey.
40,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main tumharey liye baap ki tarah hun. tumhein taalim deta hun. jab tum mein sey koi qazaey hajat ko jaey, to qibley ki taraf munh karey na peeth aur na apney daeyn haath sey istinja kerey. aur Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) teen dhelon ( sey safai karney ) ka hukm detey they aur leed aur haddi ( key sath safai ) sey mana farmatey they."
41,Hazrat Salman Farsi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney un sey kaha : tehqiq tumhara Nabi to tumhein har chiz sikhata hai yahan tak ke qazaey hajat karna bhi. unhoney farmaya : haan ! aap ney hamen mana farmaya hai ke hum qazaey hajat key waqt qibley ki taraf munh karen ya daeyn haath sey istinja karen ya teen dhelon sey kam par iktifa karen.
42,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) qazaey hajat ko gaey aur mujhey hukm diya ke main teen dheley laaun. mujhey do dheley to mil gaey teesra talash kya magar na mila. so mainey leed ka tukda utha liya aur unhein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ley aaya. aap ney dheley to ley liye, jab ke leed phenk di aur farmaya, ye to paleed hai. Imam abu Abdur-Rehman ( Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney farmaya : ( رکس ) key maana 'jinnon ki khurak' hai."
43,"Hazrat Salma bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab to dheley istimal karey to taaq istimal kar."
44,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi qazaey hajat ko jaey to apney sath teen dheley ley jaey aur un sey safai kerey. wo usey kafi hongey."
45,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab baitul-khala mein dakhil hotey to main aur merey sath mujh jaisa koi aur ladka pani ka bartan uthata, aap us pani sey istinja kartey."
46,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney aurton sey farmaya : apney khaawindon sey kaho ke wo pani sey safai kya karen. mujhey ye baat kehtey huye un sey sharam aati hai. beshak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) pani sey safai kya kartey they.
47,"Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi piye to bartan mein ( peetey huye ) saans na ley aur jab qazaey hajat karey to daeyn haath sey apni sharmgah na chhuey aur na daeyn haath sey istinja hi kerey."
48,"Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mana farmaya ke koi shakhs bartan mein saans ley, apni sharmgah ko daeyn haath sey chhuey ya daeyn haath sey safai ( istinja ) kerey."
49,"Hazrat Salman Farsi (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke mushrekin ney (mazaq) kaha : hum dekhtey hain ke tumhara Nabi tumhein qazaey hajat ka tariqa bhi batata hai. unhoney farmaya : haan ! aap ney mana farmaya hai ke koi shakhs dahaney haath sey istinja karey ya qibla rukh bethey, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi shakhs teen sey kam dhelon sey istinja na kerey."
50,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney wuzu farmaya, (us sey pehley) jab istinjey sey farigh huye to haath zamin par mala."
51,"Hazrat Jareer (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath tha. aap baitul-khala mein gaey, qazaey hajat ki, phir aap ney farmaya : aey Jareer ! pani laao. main pani laya, aap ney us sey istinja kya, phir apna haath zamin par mila. abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney farmaya : ye hadees shareek ki riwayat sey ziyada durust hai. ( wallah أعلم )"
52,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey us pani key barey mein puchha gaya jis par aam janwer aur darindey (pani peeney aur nahaney key liye) aatey jatey rehtey hain. aap ney farmaya : jab pani do matkey (ya us sey zayed) ho to wo (mazkura chizon sey) paleed nahin hota.
53,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke eik dehati aadmi ney masjide-nabwi mein peshab karna shuru kar diya. kuch log uski taraf badhey (taake usey roken. ) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey rehney do aur us ka peshab na roko. jab wo peshab sey farigh huwa to aap ney pani sey bhara huwa dol mangwaya aur peshab par baha diya. abu Abdur-Rehman (imaam Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney farmaya : (لا تزرموہ) key maana hain is ka peshab na roko.
54,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik Erabi (dehati) ney masjid mein peshab kar diya. aap ney pani ka eik dol laney ka hukm diya jisey is par baha diya gaya.
55,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik dehati masjid mein aaya aur peshab karney laga. log usey daantney lagey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey kar leney do. logon ney usey kuch na kaha yahan tak ke wo peshab sey farigh ho gaya, phir aap ney eik dol pani mangwaya aur usey is par baha diya gaya."
56,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik badwi masjid mein khada huwa aur us ney peshab karna shuru kar diya. logon ney usey ja liya to Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey kuch na kaho aur uskey peshab par pani ka eik dol baha do. tumhein narmi aur aasani key liye bheja gaya hai, na ke sakhti aur tangi key liye."
57,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs khadey pani mein peshab hargiz na karey (ho sakta hai) ke phir baad mein us sey wuzu kar ley. Hadees key raawi Auf ney kaha : Khilas ney bhi Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey aisi riwayat bayan ki hai."
58,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi thehrey pani mein bilkul peshab na karey (ho sakta hai) ke phir baad mein us sey ghusl kerey. abu Abdur-Rehman (imaam Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney farmaya : (merey Ustad) Yaqub bin Ibrahim ye hadees deenar liye baghair bayan nahin kartey they."
59,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, eik aadmi ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha ke hum samandari safar kartey hain aur apney sath thoda bahut pani ley jatey hain, chunanche agar hum us sey wuzu karen to piyasey reh jaeyn, to kya hum samandari pani sey wuzu kar liya keren? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : samandar ka pani taahir o mutah'hir hai aur is mein mar janey waley janwer halal hain."
60,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab namaz shuru farmatey to kuch der chup rehtey they. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap par merey maa baap fidaa hun. aap takbir tahreema aur qirat key darmiyan khamoshi key waqt kya padhtey hain? aap ney farmaya : main kehta hun : ( اللھم باعد بینی … … بالثلج والماء o البرد ) aey Allah ! merey aur meri ghaltiyon key darmiyan itna fasla kar dey jitna fasla tu ney mashriq aur maghrib key darmiyan kya hai. aey Allah ! mujhey meri ghaltiyon sey is tarah saaf farma dey jaisey safed kapda mail-kuchail sey saaf kya jata hai. aey Allah ! mujhey meri ghaltiyon sey barf, pani aur olon key sath dho dey."
61,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ye dua padha kartey they : اللھم ! اغسل خطایای … … من الدنس aey Allah ! meri ghaltiyon ko barf key pani aur olon sey dho dey aur merey dil ko ghaltiyon sey yun pak farma dey jaisey tu ney safed kapda mail-kuchail sey saaf rakha hai.
62,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha ke mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko eik maiyat ka janaza padhtey suna, to mainey aap ki ye dua suni, aap keh rahey they : اللھم ! اغفرلہ و ارحمہ … … من الدنس aey Allah ! us ko maaf kar dey, is par reham farma, us ko aafiyat ( salamti ) dey aur us sey darguzar farma, uski mehmani achi farma, uski qabr ko faraakh kar dey, usey pani, barf aur olon sey dho dal. aur us ko ghaltiyon sey yun pak saaf farma jaisey safed kapdey ko mail kuchail sey saaf kya jata hai."
63,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab kutta tumharey bartan mein pi ley to usey saat martaba dhona chahiye."
64,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab kutta tum mein sey kisi ka bartan chaat jaey to wo usey saat dafa dhoey."
65,Hazrat abu-Salma (Rahmatullahi Alaih) Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey usi key misl riwayat kartey hain.
66,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey kisi key bartan mein kutta munh dal kar piye, to wo us ( mashrub ) ko gira dey aur bartan saat dafa dhoey. abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney farmaya : main nahin janta ke kisi raawi ney 'tu wo usey gira dey.' key alfaz zikr karney mein Ali bin Mus'hir ki muwaafiqat ki ho. ( maqsud ye hai ke ye alfaz sirf Ali bin Mus'hir hi bayan kartey hain.)"
67,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kutton key qatl ka hukm diya, albatta shikari aur bakriyon ki hifazat key liye kutta rakhney ki ijazat di. aur aap ney farmaya : jab kutta bartan mein munh dal dey to usey saat dafa dho'o aur aathwein martaba mitti bhi malo"
68,"Kabsha bint Kaab sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) merey paas aaye, phir Kabsha ney aisey alfaz kahey jin ka matlab ye hai ke mainey unkey liye bartan mein wuzu ka pani dala. chunanche eik billi aai aur us sey pani peena shuru kar diya. unhoney billi key liye bartan jhuka diya (taake wo aasani sey pi ley) billi ney pani pi liya. Kabsha ney kaha ke unhoney mujhey dekha ke main ( herani sey) un ki taraf dekh rahi hun to kehney lagey : aey bhatiji ! kya tujhey is par tajjub hai? mainey kaha : ji haan. wo kehney lagey ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : bilashuba billi paleed nahin kyonkey ye tum par aaney janey waley nokaron aur nokraniyon ki tarah hai."
69,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke hamarey paas Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka manadi aaya aur us ney kaha ( aelan kya ) : tehqiq Allah Taala aur us ka Rasool tumhein gharelu gadhon ka gosht khaney sey roktey hain kyonkey gadhey paleed hain. (ya ye gosht haram hai.)
70,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke main kisi haddi sey gosht nochti to Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) us jagah apna munh mubarak rakhtey jahan mainey rakha tha, halanke mein haiz ki haalat mein hoti thi. aur main bartan sey pani peeti to Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) us jagah apna munh rakhtey they jahan mainey lagaya tha, halanke mein haiz ki haalat mein hoti thi."
71,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein aadmi aur aurten ikhattey wuzu kar liya kartey they.
72,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke main aur Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik hi bartan sey ghusl kya kartey they.
73,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, farmatey hain : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik mudd pani sey wuzu farma liya kartey they aur paanch mudd key sath ghusl farma liya kartey they."
74,"Hazrat Umme-Ammara binte-Kaab (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney wuzu ka irada farmaya, to aap key paas eik bartan mein pani laya gaya jo do tihai mudd key barabar tha. Shoba kehtey hain : mujhey yad hai ke aap ney (dorane-wuzu mein) apney bazu mal mal kar dhoey aur apney kanon key andruni hissey ka masah kya. aur beruni hissey key masah ka mujhey yad nahin."
75,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aamal ka aetbar niyat sey hai. har aadmi ko uski niyat key mutabiq ajr milega, chunanche jis shakhs ki hijrat Allah aur uskey Rasool ki khatir hai to us aadmi ki hijrat Allah aur uskey Rasool ki taraf samjhi jaeygi aur jis shakhs ki hijrat duniya hasil karney ya kisi aurat sey nikah karney ki khatir hai to uski hijrat us chiz ki taraf samjhi jaeygi jiski khatir us ney hijrat ki."
76,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha jabkey Asr ki namaz ka waqt ho chuka tha. logon ney wuzu key liye pani talash kya magar na mila to Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas kuch pani laya gaya. aap ney apna daste-mubarak us bartan mein rakha aur logon ko wuzu karney ka hukm diya, chunanche mainey dekha ke pani aap ki ungliyon key nichey sey ( chashmey ki tarah ) phoot raha tha yahan tak ke sab logon ney wuzu kar liya."
77,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke hum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath they. logon ko pani na mila to aap key paas pani ka eik thal laya gaya, chunanche aap ney apna haath is mein rakha. Allah ki qism ! mainey aap ki ungliyon key darmiyan sey pani phoot'ta dekha. aap farmatey they : aao us pak pani par aur Allah azz-w-jall ki barkat ki taraf. Aamash kehtey hain : Salim bin Abu-Ja'ad ney mujhey bataya ke mainey Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha ke tum us din kitney they? unhoney farmaya : pandarah so."
78,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key kuch sahaba ney wuzu ka pani talash kya to Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tum mein sey kisi key paas kuch pani hai? (pani laya gaya) to aap ney apna haath pani mein rakh diya aur farmaya : Allah ka naam ley kar wuzu karo. chunanche mainey aap ki ungliyon key darmiyan sey pani nikalta dekha yahan tak ke sab ney wuzu kar liya. (Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) key shagrid) sabit ney kaha ke mainey Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : aap key khayal mein wo kitney hongey? to unhoney farmaya : taqriban satar (70).
79,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke mainey ghazwa tabuk mein wuzu key doran mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key aazaaey mubarka par pani dala, phir aap ney mozon par masah farmaya. abu Abdur-Rehman (imaam Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) farmatey hain ke Imam Malik (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney (ibaad bin Zaid key baad) Urwa bin Mughira ka zikr nahin kya."
80,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke kya main tumhein Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key wuzu key barey mein na bataun ? phir (ye keh kar) unhoney wuzu key angon ko eik eik dafa dhoya.
81,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma ney wuzu key angon ko teen teen baar dhoya aur wo is kaam ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf mansub kartey they.
82,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke hum eik safar mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath they ke aap ney ( mutawajjeh karney key liye) apni chhadi meri pusht sey lagai, phir aap eik taraf ko chaley main bhi aap key sath chala yahan tak ke aap eik ( munasib ) jagah pahunchey. aap ney apna oont bithaya aur pedal chal diye yahan tak ke mujh sey ojhal ho gaey. phir wapis tashrif laye aur farmaya : terey paas pani hai? merey paas mera mishkeeza tha. main wo aap key paas ley aaya aur mainey pani dalna shuru kya. aap ney apney haath aur chehra dhoya. bazu dhoney lagey to aap par tang aastinon wala shami jubba tha. aap ney apna haath jubbey key nichey sey nikala. is tarah apna chehra aur bazu dhoey aur apney kuch sar ( peshani ) aur baqi pagdi par masah kya. ibn Aun ney kaha : jis tarah mein chahta hun mujhey is tarah yad nahin hai. phir aap ney apney mozon par masah kya. phir aap ney farmaya : to bhi qazaey hajat kar ley. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey hajat nahin hai. phir hum ( qafley key paas ) aaye to Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) logon key aagey khadey imaamat kara rahey they aur subh ki eik rakat padha chukey they. mainey unhein ittilaa dena chahi, magar aap ney mujhey rok diya. jo namaz hamney ( jamaat key sath ) pai padh li aur jo guzar chuki thi, usey ( baad mein) ada kar liya."
83,"Hazrat Abu-Aus (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha, aap ney (apni hatheliyon par) teen dafa pani bahaya."
84,"Hazrat Humran bin Aban sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha. aap ney wuzu kya aur apney haathon par teen dafa pani dala aur unhein dhoya. phir aap ney kulli ki aur naak mein pani chadhaya. phir apna chehra teen martaba dhoya. phir apna daayan bazu kohni tak teen dafa dhoya. phir baayan bazu bhi isi tarah dhoya. phir apney sar ka masah kya. phir apna daayan paaun teen dafa dhoya aur phir baayan paaun bhi isi tarah dhoya. phir kehney lagey : mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha, aap ney merey wuzu ki tarah wuzu kya, phir aap ney farmaya : jo shakhs merey is wuzu ki tarah wuzu kerey. phir do rakatein is tarah ada karey ke apney dil mein koi baat na kerey. uskey guzishta sab gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain."
85,"Humran sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha, aap ney pani mangwaya aur bartan sey apney dono haathon par pani dala aur unhein teen dafa dhoya. phir apna daayan haath pani mein dakhil kya aur kulli ki aur naak mein pani chadhaya. phir apna chehra teen dafa dhoya aur apney dono bazuon ko kohniyon tak teen martaba dhoya. phir apney sar ka masah kya. phir dono paaun teen teen dafa dhoey. phir unhoney kaha : mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha, aap ney merey is wuzu jaisa wuzu kya aur farmaya : jo shakhs merey is wuzu jaisa wuzu kerey. phir khada ho kar do rakat namaz padhey aur uski adaegi mein apney dil mein koi baat na kerey. uskey guzishta tamam gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain."
86,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi shakhs wuzu kerey. to usey chahiye ke apni naak mein pani daley aur phir ( usey ) achi tarah saaf kerey.
87,"Hazrat laqeet bin Sabra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey wuzu key ( sahih tareeqey ) key barey mein bataeyn. aap ney farmaya : wuzu key angon ko mukammal ( achi tarah ) dho aur naak mein pani dalney mein mubaalgha kar, siwaye uskey ke to rozey sey ho."
88,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs wuzu kerey. usey chahiye ke wo naak jhaadey. aur jo shakhs ( istinjey key liye) dheley istimal kerey. usey chahiye ke wo taaq istimal kerey.
89,Hazrat Salma bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab to wuzu karey to naak jhaad aur jab to ( qazaey hajat key baad ) dheley istimal karey to taaq istimal kar.
90,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi shakhs neend sey jaagey aur wuzu karey to wo teen baar naak ko jhaadey kyonkey shetan uski naak ki jad mein raat guzaarta hai.
91,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke unhoney wuzu ka pani mangwaya, phir us sey kulli ki aur naak mein pani chadhaya aur apney baain haath sey jhaada. ye kaam teen dafa kya, phir farmaya : ye hai Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka wuzu."
92,"Hazrat Abd Khair sey manqul hai ke hum Hazrat Ali bin Abu-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaye. aap namaz padh chukey they. aap ney wuzu ka pani mangwaya. hamney kaha : aap us sey kya kerengey jabkey aap to namaz padh chukey hain? darasal aap hamen wuzu sikhana chahtey they, chunanche aap key paas eik pani ka bartan aur eik thal laya gaya. aap ney bartan sey haath par pani dala aur usey teen dafa dhoya. phir usi hatheli sey teen dafa kulli ki aur naak mein pani chadhaya jis sey pani letey they, phir apna chehra teen baar dhoya, apna daayan bazu teen dafa dhoya aur apna baayan bazu teen dafa dhoya aur eik baar apney sar ka masah kya, phir apna daayan paaun teen dafa dhoya aur baayan paaun bhi teen dafa dhoya, phir farmaya : jo Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka wuzu janna pasand karta hai, wo jaan ley ke wo aisa tha."
93,"Hazrat Abd Khair sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key paas eik kursi laee gaee, aap is par beth gaey, phir pani ka eik thal mangwaya, aap ney apney haathon par teen dafa pani undela, phir eik hi chullu sey kulli ki aur naak mein pani chadhaya. ye teen baar kya. aur apna chehra teen dafa dhoya aur apney bazu teen teen dafa dhoey, phir kuch pani liya aur sar ka masah kya, Shoba ney eik baar peshani sey ley kar sar key aakhir tak ishara kya, phir kaha : mujhey malum nahin ke phir (hathon ko) lotaya tha ya nahin. aur teen teen dafa apney paaun dhoey, phir farmaya : jo shakhs pasand karta hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka wuzu dekhey to wo jaan ley ke ye aap ka wuzu hai. Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman ( Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) likhtey hain : (sanad mein) ye ghalati hai. sahih naam Khalid bin Alqama hai na ke Malik bin Arfata."
94,"Hazrat Abd Khair sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha, aap ney kursi mangwai, is par bethey, phir eik thal mein pani mangwaya aur apney haath teen dafa dhoey, phir eik hi haath sey teen dafa kulli ki aur naak mein pani chadhaya, phir apna chehra aur bazu teen teen dafa dhoey, phir apna haath bartan mein duboya aur apney sar ka masah kya, phir apney paaun teen teen dafa dhoey, phir farmaya : jo shakhs Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka wuzu dekhna pasand kerey. to wo jaan ley ke ye aap ka wuzu hai."
95,"Hazrat Husain bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke merey walid Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney mujh sey wuzu ka pani mangwaya, mainey pani aap key qarib kya, aap ney pehley apni hatheliyan teen dafa dhoin pehley us sey ke unhein pani mein dakhil keren, phir aap ney teen dafa kulli ki aur teen dafa naak saaf kya. phir chehra teen martaba dhoya, phir daeyn haath ko kohni samet teen dafa dhoya, phir baain ko isi tarah dhoya, phir apney sar ka eik dafa masah kya, phir daayan paaun takhnon samet teen dafa dhoya, phir isi tarah baayan dhoya, phir sidhey khadey ho gaey aur farmaya mujhey bartan pakdao. mainey aap ko bartan pakdaaya jis mein aap key wuzu sey bacha huwa pani tha. aap ney wo khadey khadey piya. mujhey tajjub huwa. jab aap ney mujhey dekha, to farmaya : tajjub na kar, kyonkey mainey terey nana Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap isi tarah kartey they jis tarah tu ney mujhey kartey dekha hai. aap (Hazrat Ali ) ka ishara wuzu aur khadey ho kar wuzu ka pani peeney ki taraf tha."
96,"Hazrat Abu-Haiya bin Qais sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke aap ney wuzu ka aaghaz kya, to apni hatheliyon ko dhoya yahan tak ke unhein achi tarah saaf kya, phir teen dafa kulli ki aur phir teen martaba naak mein pani chadhaya, teen martaba apna chehra dhoya aur teen teen dafa apney bazu dhoey, phir apney sar ka masah kya, phir takhnon samet apney paaun dhoey, phir khadey huye aur apney wuzu sey bacha huwa pani liya aur khadey khadey piya, phir farmaya, mainey achcha samjha ke tumhein dikhaaun ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka wuzu kaisa tha?"
97,"Hazrat Amr bin Yahya Mazni apney walid sey riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid bin Aasim (Raziallahu anhu), jo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sahabi aur Amr bin Yahya key nana they, sey guzarish ki : kya aap mujhey dikha saktey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) wuzu kaisey farmaya kartey they? Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : han, phir unhoney wuzu ka pani mangwaya aur apney haath par dala aur dono haath do do martaba dhoey, phir teen dafa kulli ki aur naak mein pani chadhaya, phir teen dafa apna chehra dhoya, phir apney dono bazu do do martaba kohniyon samet dhoey, phir dono haathon sey apney sar ka masah kya ke dono haathon ko aagey peechey laye, masah ki ibtida (shuruat) sar key agley hissey sey ki, phir haathon ko apni guddi ki taraf ley gaey, phir wapis laye yahan tak ke us jagah pahunch gaey jahan sey masah ki ibtida (shuruat) ki thi, phir apney dono paaun dhoey."
98,"Hazrat Yahya Mazni sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid bin Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) sey guzarish ki aur aap Amr bin Yahya key nana they : kya aap mujhey dikha saktey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) wuzu kaisey farmaya kartey they? Hazrat Abdullah ney kaha, haan. phir aap ney wuzu ka pani mangwaya aur apney daeyn haath par dala aur dono haath do do martaba dhoey, phir teen dafa kulli ki aur naak mein pani chadhaya, phir teen dafa apna chehra dhoya, phir apney dono bazu do do martaba kohniyon samet dhoey. phir dono haathon sey apney sar ka masah kya is tarah ke dono haath aagey peechey laye, masah ki ibtida (shuruat) sar key agley hissey sey ki, phir haathon ko apni guddi ki taraf ley gaey, phir wapis laye yahan tak ke us jagah pahunch gaey jahan sey masah ki ibtida (shuruat) ki thi, phir apney dono paaun dhoey."
99,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) jinhein khuwab mein Azan dikhlai gaee thi, sey manqul hai, kehtey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko wuzu kartey dekha, chunanche aap ney apna chehra teen dafa dhoya aur dono bazu do dafa dhoey. paaun ko bhi do martaba dhoya aur apney sar ka masah do dafa kya."
100,"Hazrat Abu Abdullah Salim Sablan Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat kartey hain, aur Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) un ki amanat daari sey bahut khush thin aur un sey ujrat par kaam karwaya karti thin wo kehtey hain ke mujhey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney dikhlaayaa ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kaisey wuzu farmaya kartey they. unhoney teen dafa kulli ki aur naak jhaada aur apna chehra teen dafa dhoya, phir apna daayan aur baayan haath (bazu) teen,teen dafa dhoya, phir Hazrat Aaisha ney apna haath sar key agley hissa par rakha aur peechhey tak purey sar ka eik dafa masah kiya, phir unhoney apney haath apney kanon par pherey  phir rukhsaaron par pherey. Salim ney kaha : main jab makatib tha to aap key paas aaya karta tha, wo mujh sey parda nahin karti thin balke merey samney beth kar mujh sey baaten kiya karti thin yahan tak ke main eik din unkey paas aaya aur mainey kaha : aey Ummul-mominn ! merey liye barkat ki dua farmaiye. wo kehney lagin : kya baat hai? mainey kaha : Allah Taala ney mujhey azad farma diya hai. wo kehney lagin : Allah Taala tumharey liye barkat farmaey. uskey baad parda latka liya aur us din key baad mainey unhein nahin dekha."
101,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko wuzu kartey dekha, chunanche aap ney haath dhoey, phir aap ney eik chullu sey kulli ki aur naak mein pani chadhaya aur eik baar apna chehra dhoya aur apney dono bazu eik eik dafa dhoey aur apney sar aur dono kanon ka eik dafa masah kiya. ( Hadees key raawi ) Abdul-Azeez kehtey hain : mujhey ibn Ajlaan sey sun'ney waley ney khabar di ke is hadees mein ye alfaz bhi hain : aur apney dono paaun dhoey."
102,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney wuzu farmaya, chunanche eik chullu pani liya us sey kulli ki aur naak mein pani chadhaya, phir eik chulllu pani liya aur us sey apna chehra dhoya, phir eik chullu pani liya aur us sey apna daayan haath dhoya, phir eik chullu pani liya aur us sey baayan haath dhoya, phir apney sar aur kanon ka masah kiya. kanon key andruni janib ka masah shahadat ki ungliyon sey aur berooni (baahri) janib ka angootheyn sey kiya. phir eik chulllu pani liya aur us sey daayan paaun dhoya, phir eik chullu pani liya aur us sey baayan paaun dhoya."
103,"Hazrat Abdullah Sanaabihi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab momin banda wuzu kartey huye kulli karta hai to uskey munh ki ghaltiyaan uskey munh sey nikal jati hain, phir jab wo naak jhadta hai to naak ki ghaltiyaan naak sey nikal jati hain, phir jab wo munh dhota hai to chehrey ki ghaltiyaan chehrey sey yahan tak ke aakhon ki palkon sey nikal jati hain, phir jab wo apney haath dhota hai to haathon ki ghaltiyaan uskey haathon sey yahan tak ke haathon key naakhunon key nichey sey nikal jati hain, phir jab wo apney sar ka masah karta hai to uskey sar ki ghaltiyaan sar sey yahan tak ke uskey kanon sey nikal jati hain, phir jab wo apney paaun dhota hai to uskey paaun ki ghaltiyaan paaun sey yahan tak ke paaun key naakhunon key nichey sey nikal jati hain, phir us ka masjid ki taraf chalna aur uski namaz (un do kamon ka sawab) uskey liye zayed hotey hain. Fateeba ney yun bayan kiya (عن الصنابحی ان النبی padhi. قال) yani Sanaabihi sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya."
104,Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko mozon aur pagdi par masah kartey dekha.
105,Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke mainey Rasool Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko mozon par masah kartey dekha hai.
106,Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko pagdi aur mozon par masah kartey dekha hai.
107,Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hua) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney wuzu kiya aur aap ney apni peshani pagdi aur mozon par masah farmaya. (Hadees key raawi) Bakr ney kaha : tehqiq mainey ye hadees baraahe-raast Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) key betey sey bhi suni hai.
108,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke (eik safar mein) Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (logon sey) peechhey reh gaey. main bhi aap key sath raha. jab aap qazaey hajat (peshaab-paakhaaney) sey farigh huye to farmaya : kya terey paas pani hai? chunanche main aap key paas lota laya to aap ney apni hatheliyan dhoein aur chehra dhoya, phir apney bazuon sey kapda hataney lagey magar jubbey ki aasteen tang thi to aap ney jubbey ko kandhon par dal liya  phir apney bazu dhoey aur apni peshani pagdi aur mozon par masah farmaya."
109,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke do baaten aisi hain jin ki baabat mein kabhi kisi sey nahin poochhunga  jab ke mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey unka khud mushaahida kiya (dekha) hai. eik to ye ke hum aap key sath eik safar mein they to aap qazaey hajat (zarurat se faraghat) key liye gaey, phir wapis tashrif la kar wuzu kiya aur apni peshani aur pagdi key dono traf ka masah farmaya aur apney mozon par masah farmaya. unhoney kaha : (dusri baat) Imam ka apne logon mein sey kisi aadmi key peechhey (us ki iqtida (pairvi) mein) namaz padhna. to mainey us ka bhi Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey mushaahida kya. aap eik safar mein they ke namaz ka waqt ho gaya aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko (qazaey hajat (zarurat se faraghat) sey wapsi mein) der ho gaee. sahaba ney jamaat khadi kar li aur Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ko aagey kar liya. unhoney namaz padhaai. (us doran mein) Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bhi tashrif ley aaye aur aap ney ibne Auf (Raziallahu anhu) key peechhey namaz padhi. jab Abdur-Rehman bin Auf ney salam pheraa to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uthey aur baqiya namaz ada ki."
110,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Abul-Qaasim Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is eidi key liye (jo khushk reh jaey ) halaakat yani aag hai.
111,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kuchh logon ko wuzu kartey dekha. aap ney dekha ke un ki eidiyaan khushk hain to aap ney farmaya : un ediyon key liye aag ki tabahi hai, wuzu achchhi tarah kiya karo."
112,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jahan tak mumkin hota wuzu farmaney joota pehan'ney aur kanghi karney mein daeyn taraf sey ibtida (shuruat) karna pasand farmatey. Shoba kehtey hain : mainey Ash-as ko Waasit mein kehtey huye suna ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tamam umoor (kaamon) mein daeyn taraf pasand kartey they. phir mainey unhein koofa mein kehtey huye suna ke aap hasabe-istataat daeyn janib pasand kartey they.
113,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abu-Qirdad Qaisi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke main eik safar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath tha. aap key paas kuchh pani laya gaya to aap ney bartan sey apney haathon par pani dala aur unhein eik dafa dhoya, phir apney chehrey aur dono baazuon ko eik eik dafa dhoya. aur apney dono paaun apney dono haathon sey dhoey."
114,Hazrat Laqeet bin Sabra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab to wuzu karey to achchhi tarah wuzu kar aur ungliyon key darmiyan khilaal kar.
115,"Hazrat Abu-Haiyyi Waadai sey riwayat hai, wo bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko wuzu kartey dekha ke aap ney apni hatheliyon ko teen martaba dhoya, teen martaba kulli ki, teen martaba naak mein pani chadhaya, apna chehra teen martaba aur apney bazu bhi teen teen martaba dhoey. apney sar ka masah kiya aur apney pairon ko teen teen dafa dhoya, phir farmaya : ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka wuzu hai."
116,"Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) key azad karda ghulam Hazrat Humran sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, unhoney bayan kiya ke Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney wuzu ka pani mangwaya aur wuzu kiya, apni hatheliyan teen dafa dhoein. phir kulli ki aur naak mein pani chadhaya, phir chehra teen dafa dhoya, phir daayan bazu kohni samet teen martaba dhoya, phir baayan bazu bhi isi tarah dhoya, phir apney sar ka masah kiya, phir apna daayan paaun takhnon samet teen martaba dhoya, phir baayan paaun isi tarah dhoya, phir kaha ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha, aap ney merey is wuzu ki tarah wuzu kiya, phir unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney merey is wuzu ki tarah wuzu kiya, phir khadey ho kar do rakatein is tarah ada karey ke un ki adaegi key doran mein apney dil sey koi baat na karey to uskey pehley sab gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain."
117,Hazrat Ubaid bin Juraij farmatey hain ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey kaha : main dekhta hun ke aap saaf chamdey key jootay pehantey hain aur un mein wuzu kartey hain. unhoney farmaya : mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye pehantey aur un mein wuzu kartey dekha hai.
118,Hazrat Jareer bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke unhoney wuzu kiya aur apney mozon par masah kiya. unhein kaha gaya ke kya aap mozon par masah kartey hain? to unhoney farmaya : mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko masah kartey huye dekha hai. Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) key shagirdon ko Jareer ki ye riwayat bahut pasand aati thi kyonkey Hazrat Jareer (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat sey thoda arsa pehley Islam laye they.
119,Hazrat Amr bin Umayya Zamri (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap ney wuzu kiya aur apney mozon par masah kiya.
120,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) asawaaf mein dakhil huye to aap qazaey hajat (zarurat se faraghat) key liye gaey, phir bahar nikley to Usama ney kaha : mainey Bilal sey puchha ke aap ney kya kiya? Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) qazaey hajat (zarurat se faraghat) key liye gaey, phir wuzu farmaya, apney chehrey aur dono haathon ko dhoya, apney sar ka masah farmaya aur mozon par masah farmaya, phir namaz padhi."
121,Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mozon par masah farmaya.
122,Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mozon par masah key barey mein farmaya ke is mein koi harj nahin.
123,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) qazaey hajat (zarurat se faraghat) key liye nikley chunanche jab wapis tashrif laye to main pani ka lota ley kar aap ko mila aur mainey aap key wuzu key angon par pani dala to aap ney hatheliyan dhoin phir apna chehra dhoya, phir bazu dhoney lagey  magar jubba tang tha, chunanche aap ney dono haath jubbey key nichey sey nikaley aur unhein dhoya, phir mozon par masah kiya, phir aap ney hamein namaz padhaai."
124,Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key barey mein bayan kartey hain ke aap qazaey hajat (zarurat se faraghat) key liye nikley to Mughira bhi pani ka lota ley kar aap key sath gaey. jab aap qazaey hajat (zarurat se faraghat) sey farigh huye to unhoney wuzu key angon par pani bahaayaa aap ney wuzu kiya aur apney mozon par masah farmaya.
125,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke main eik safar mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath tha to aap ney farmaya : aey Mughira ! tum thehro. aur aey logo ! tum chalo. main thehar gaya aur merey paas pani ka eik lota tha aur log chaley gaey, phir Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) qazaey hajat (zarurat se faraghat) key liye gaey jab wapis tashrif laye to mainey aap key wuzu key angon par pani bahana shuru kar diya. aap par eik Romi jubba tha jiski aasteenein tang thin. aap ney apna bazu aasteen sey nikalna chaha magar aasteen tang thi to aap ney apna haath jubbey key nichey sey nikal liya chunanche aap ney apna chehra aur bazu dhoey aur sar ka masah kiya aur apney mozon par masah farmaya."
126,"Hazrat Safwan bin Asaal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein ijazat di ke jab hum musafir hon to teen din raat tak apney mozey na utaaren (balke masah kartey rahen)."
127,"Hazrat Zar bin Habish sey riwayat hai, wo bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Safwan bin Asaal (Raziallahu anhu) sey mozon par masah karney key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamein hukm detey they ke jab hum musafir hon to teen din tak (zarurat se faraghat) aur neend ki wajeh sey mozey na utaaren balke un par masah kartey rahen magar janabat (hambistari ke baad naapaaki ki haalat) ki bina par utaarney hongey."
128,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney musafir key liye teen din raat aur muqeem key liye eik din raat mozon par masah ki muddat muqarrar farmaee.
129,"Shureh bin Haani sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, farmatey hain ke mainey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey mozon par masah key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Ali key paas jaao bilashuba wo us masley ko mujh sey ziyada jantey hain. main Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key paas gaya aur un sey maseh key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamein irshad farmatey they ke muqeem eik din raat aur musafir teen din raat mozon par masah kar sakta hai."
130,"Hazrat Nazaal bin Sabra sey riwayat hai, wo bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke aap ney Zohar ki namaz padhi phir logon ki zarooriyaat puri karney key liye beth gaey. jab Asr ka waqt huwa to aap key paas pani ka eik thal laya gaya. aap ney us sey eik chullu pani liya aur apney chehrey 'bazuon' sar aur paaun par mil liya phir bacha huwa pani khadey ho kar pi liya aur farmaya ke log isey napasand kartey hain jabkey mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko aisa kartey dekha hai aur ye us shakhs ka wuzu hai jis ka pehla wuzu nahin tootaa."
131,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas (pani ka) eik chhota sa bartan laya gaya aur aap ney wuzu farmaya. shagrid ney puchha ke kya Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) har namaz key liye naya wuzu farmatey they? unhoney farmaya : haan. shagrid ney kaha aur aap log yani sahaba bhi? aap ney farmaya : hum to jab tak be-wuzu nahin hotey they, namazein padhtey rehtey they aur eik wuzu sey kaee kaee namazein padh liya kartey they."
132,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) baitul-khala sey bahar tashrif laye aur aap ko khana pesh kiya gaya. sahaba ney puchha ke hum aap key liye wuzu ka pani na laaeyn? aap ney farmaya, mujhey wuzu ka hukm sirf us waqt hai jab main namaz key liye uthoon."
133,Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) har namaz key liye wuzu farmaya kartey they. jab fateh Makka ka din tha to aap ney kaee namazein eik wuzu sey padhein. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : aap ney aisa kaam kiya hai jo aap is sey pehley nahin kartey they. aap ney farmaya : aey umr ! mainey jaan boojh kar aisey kiya hai.
134,Hazrat Sufiyan Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab wuzu farmatey to pani ka eik chullu letey aur usey aisey kartey. Shoba ney is ka tariqa bayan kartey huye kaha : yani apni sharmgaah par chhidak letey. mainey ye baat Ibrahim Nakh'i ko batai to unhoney isey bahut saraahaa. Shekh ibne Suni (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney kaha : (sanad mein mazkur) hukm sey murad Hukm bin Sufiyan Saqafi hain (Hukm bin Sufiyan ko baaz raawiyon ney Sufiyan bin Hakam bhi kaha hai. ye Sahabi hain aur in sey sirf yehi eik hadees manqul (naqal hui) hai).
135,"Hazrat Hukm bin Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, wo bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap ney wuzu kiya aur apni sharmgah par chheentey maarey. ustaad Ahmed bin Harab ney ( ونضح فرجہ ) key bajaey ( فنضح فرجہ ) kaha."
136,"Hazrat Abu-Haiya sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha, aap ney wuzu key angon ko teen teen dafa dhoya, phir khadey ho kar wuzu sey bacha huwa pani piya aur farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney aisey hi kiya jaisey mainey kiya."
137,Hazrat Abu-Juhaifa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko (Makka key maqam) Bat'haa mein dekha. Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) aap key wuzu sey bacha huwa pani ley kar (khemey sey) nikley. log tezi sey un ki taraf bhagey. mujhey bhi is mein sey kuchh pani mil gaya. phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key liye eik neza gaad diya gaya aur aap ney (usey samney rakh kar) logon ko namaz padhaai. gadhey kuttey aur aurten aap key (sutrey key) aagey sey guzarti thin.
138,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke main bimar ho gaya to Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) meri bimar pursi key liye tashrif laye to mujhey be-hosh paya. aap ney wuzu farmaya aur wuzu ka pani mujh par dala.
139,"Hazrat Abu-Mulaih apney walid mohtaram sey bayan kartey hain, unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala koi namaz baghair tahaarat (wuzu) key qubul nahin farmata aur na haram maal sey sadqa qubul farmata hai."
140,"Amr bin Shuaib apney baap aur wo apney dada sey bayan kartey hain ke eik dehati Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya. wo aap sey wuzu ka tariqa poochhta tha. aap ney usey teen teen dafa wuzu key ang dho kar dikhaye phir farmaya : wuzu is tarah hai. jisney is sey ziyada kiya, us ney bura kiya, had sey badha aur zulm ka kaam kiya."
141,"Abdullah bin Ubedullah bin Abbas kehtey hain ke hum Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma key paas bethey they ke aap ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney teen chizon key siwa hamein logon sey alag koi khususi hukm nahin diya. aap ney hamein hukm diya ke hum wuzu mukammal aur achchhi tarah keren, sadqa na khaeyn aur gadhon ki ghodiyon sey jufti na karaaein."
142,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wuzu mukammal aur achchhi tarah karo."
143,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya main tumhein un chizon ki khabar na dun jin key sath Allah Taala ghaltiyaan mitata aur darjaat buland farmata hai? (Sahaaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kiya Allah key Rasool kyon nahin? aap ney farmaya :) mashaqqat aur na-chahtey huye wuzu mukammal aur achchhi tarah karna  masjid ki taraf door sey chal kar jana aur namaz key baad agli namaz ka (masjid mein beth kar) intizar karna. ye hai ribaat (sarhad par hathiyaar-band hokar choksi ke saath baithnaa). ye hai ribaat. ye hai ribaat."
144,"Hazrat Aasim bin Sufiyan Saqafi (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey riwayat hai ke hum salaasil (eik chashmey ka naam) ki jang ko gaey magar jang na mil saki. (kyonkey Aasim aur unkey kuchh sathi baad mein pahunchey they, chunanche) wo log kuchh arsa mahaaz par morcha zan rahey (lekin jang ki dobara nobat na aai) phir wo Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) key paas lot aaye. us waqt unkey paas Hazrat Abu-Ayyub aur Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir Raziallahu anhuma bethey they. Aasim ney kaha : Abu-Ayyub ! us saal hum jihad sey mehroom reh gaey, hamein batlaya gaya hai ke jo aadmi chaar masjidon (Masjide-Haram, Masjide-Nabwi, Masjide Aqsaa aur Masjide Qubaa) mein namaz padhey  uskey gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain. Hazrat Abu-Ayyub (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : aey bhateejey ! main tujhey is sey aasan tar kaam batata hun. mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo shakhs wuzu karey jis tarah hukm hai aur namaz padhey jaisey usey hukm diya gaya hai to uskey pehley tamam gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain. (phir Aqba ki taraf mutawajjeh ho kar farmaya : ) aey Aqba ! kya aisey hi hai? unhoney farmaya : haan."
145,"Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney is tarah wuzu mukammal kiya jis tarah Allah Taala ney usey hukm diya hai to uskey liye paanch namazein darmiyan waley gunahon ka kaffara bin jaaeyngi."
146,"Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, wo bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo aadmi wuzu karey aur achchhi tarah kerey. phir namaz padhey uskey liye agli namaz tak key gunah maaf farma diye jatey hain yahan tak ke us namaz ko padh ley."
147,"Hazrat Abu Amaama Baahli (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke mainey Hazrat Amr bin Abasa (Raziallahu anhu) ko farmatey suna, wo keh rahey they ke mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! wuzu kaisey kiya jaey? (ya wuzu ka maqam kya hai?) aap ney farmaya : wuzu ka martaba ye hai ke jab to wuzu mein apni hatheliyan dhota hai aur unhein achchhi tarah saaf karta hai to teri ghaltiyaan terey naakhunon aur poron key darmiyan sey nikal jati hain, phir jab to kulli karta hai aur apney nathnon ko saaf karta hai, apna chehra aur kohniyon samet bazu dhota hai, apney sar ka masah karta hai aur takhnon samet paaun dhota hai to to apni aksar ghaltiyon sey dhul jata hai, phir agar to Allah Taala key samney apna chehra rakhey (namaz padhey) to to apni ghaltiyon sey is tarah nikal aata hai jaisey aaj hi tujhey teri maa ney jana ho. abu-Umama kehtey hain ke mainey kaha : aey Amr bin Abasa ! ghor farmaiye ! aap kya keh rahey hain? kya ye sab kuchchh eik majlis mein mil jata hai? wo farmaney lagey : Allah ki qism ! tehqiq mein boodha ho gaya hun aur meri maut qarib aa gaee hai. main faqir nahin ke (maal hasil karney key liye) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par jhoot boloon. Allah ki qism ! yaqinan merey kanon ney ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey suni hai aur merey dil ney isey yad rakha hai."
148,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo aadmi wuzu karey aur achchhi tarah kerey. phir ye padhey : (أشھد أن لا الہ الا اللہ … … … عبدہ و رسولہ), ""main gawahi deta hun ke Allah Taala key siwa koi bar-haq mabood nahin aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur Rasool hain. uskey liye jannat key aathon darwazey chaupat khol diye jatey hain. jis darwazey sey chahey dakhil ho jaaey."
149,"Hazrat Abu-Haazim sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke main Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key peechhey tha aur wo namaz key liye wuzu kar rahey they. wo bazu dho rahey they yahan tak ke baghlon tak pahunch gaey. mainey kaha : aey Abu-Hurera ! ye kaisa wuzu hai? aap farmaney lagey : ooh, Farrukh ki nasal ! (Ajamiyon (ghair Arab) ! ) tum yahan ho? agar mujhey ilm hota ke tum yahan ho to main hergiz ye wuzu na karta. mainey apney Khaleel (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna hai : momin ka zewar wahan tak pahuncheyga jahan tak wuzu ka pani pahuncheyga."
150,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) qabristaan ki taraf gaey aur farmaya : tum par salamti ho, aey momin logon key shehar (aey momin logon key shehar key baasiyo ! ) aur yaqinan hum Insha-Allah tumhein aa milengey. meri khahish thi ke main apney bhaiyon ko dekh leta. sahaba ney arz ki ke aey Allah key Rasool ! kya hum aap key bhai nahin? aap ney farmaya : tum to merey sahaba ho. merey bhai wo hain jo abhi tak paida nahin huye aur main Hoze-Kausar par unka paish-rau hunga. sahaba ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap apni ummat key un logon ko kaisey pahchaaneingey jo aap key baad aayengey? aap ney farmaya : bataao agar eik aadmi key ghodey safed maathe aur safed haath paaun waley hon jabkey doosrey ghodey khalis siyah hon to kya wo apney ghodon ko nahin pehchan leyga. unhoney kaha : kyon nahin (zarur pehchan leyga.) aap ney farmaya : bilashuba wo log qiyamat key din roshan chehron aur chamaktey haath paaon key sath aayengey aur main Hoze-Kausar par unka paish-rau hunga."
151,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs wuzu karey aur achchhi tarah behtareen wuzu karey, phir do rakat is tarah padhey ke dil aur chehrey ki (zaahiran aur andruni) tawajjoh unhi (do rak'at) ki taraf ho, uskey liye jannat wajib ho qaee."
152,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke mujhey mazi bahut aaya karti thi. chunkey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki sahab-zaadi merey nikah mein thi, lihaza mujhey aap sey ye masla poochhtey sharam aati thi, chunanche mainey apney pehlu mein bethey eik shakhs sey kaha ke aap sey (ye masla) poochho. us ney aap sey puchha to aap ney farmaya : uskey nikalney sey wuzu wajib hota hai (ghusl nahin)."
153,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke mainey Hazrat Miqdaad (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : jab koi aadmi apni biwi sey dil lagi karey aur usey mazi aa jaey jab ke us ney jima (sambhog) nahin kiya (to wo kya karey)? aap ye masla Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey poochhen kyonkey aap ki beti merey nikah mein hai, is liye mujhey sharam aati hai. Hazrat Miqdaad ney puchha to aap ney farmaya : wo apni sharmgah waghera dho ley aur namaz wala wuzu kar ley."
154,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, wo bayan kartey hain ke mujhey mazi bahut aaya karti thi, chunanche aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki beti key merey nikah mein honey ki wajeh sey mainey Hazrat Ammaar bin Yaasar (Raziallahu anha) ko kaha ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey is masley ki baabat poochhen to aap ney farmaya : is (mazi) sey wuzu kafi hai."
155,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai, unhoney Hazrat Ammaar (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha ke wo Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey mazi key barey mein poochhen. aap ney farmaya : wo apni sharmgah waghera dho ley aur wuzu kar ley."
156,"Hazrat Miqdaad bin Aswad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney us sey kaha ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey us aadmi key barey mein poochhen jo apni biwi sey qarib hota hai to us sey mazi nikalti hai to is par kya wajib hai? chunkey aap ki beti merey nikah mein hai, is liye mujhey ye poochhtey huye sharam aati hai, chunanche mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey is barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi ye soorate-haal paaey to wo apni sharmgah dho ley aur namaz wala wuzu kar ley."
157,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, wo bayan kartey hain ke mujhey Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ki wajeh sey sharam aati thi ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey mazi key barey mein poochhun chunanche mainey Miqdaad bin Aswad (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha to unhoney aap sey puchha. aap ney farmaya : is mein wuzu hai."
158,"Hazrat Zar bin Habish sey riwayat hai, wo bayan kartey hain ke main eik aadmi key paas gaya jinhein Safwan bin Asaal kaha jata tha. main (intizar mein) unkey darwazey par beth gaya. aap bahar tashrif laye to puchha : kaisey aaye ho? mainey kaha : talabe-ilm key liye. unhoney farmaya : farishtey talibe-ilm key talabe-ilm par raza mandi ka izhar kartey huye apney par jhukaatey hain. phir unhoney puchha : tum kya poochhnaa chahtey ho? mainey kaha : mozon key barey mein. unhoney farmaya : jab hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath (kisi safar mein) hotey they to aap hamein farmatey they ke hum teen din tak peshab ya paakhaaney aur neend ki wajeh sey mozey na utaaren lekin janabat (sambhog ki naapaaki) ki wajeh sey utaarney hongey."
159,"Hazrat Safwan bin Asaal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab hum kisi safar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath hotey they to aap hamein irshad farmatey they ke hum teen din tak peshab, paakhaaney aur neend ki wajeh sey mozey na utaaren lekin janabat (sambhog ki naapaaki) ki wajeh sey utaarney padeyngey."
160,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, wo bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas us aadmi ka masla pesh kiya gaya, jo namaz key doran mein koi chiz mehsus karey (usey shak padey ke hawa khaarij hui hai to kya kerey)?  to aap ney farmaya : wo namaz sey na nikley yahan tak ke boo paey ya (hawa nikalney ki) aawaz suney."
161,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi shakhs neend sey jaagey to apna haath bartan mein na daley yahan tak ke pehley is par teen dafa pani dal kar dho ley kyonkey wo nahin janta ke uskey haath ney raat kahan basar ki (raat bhar kahan kahan lagta raha hai)."
162,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab kisi shakhs ko namaz mein ungh aaney lagey to wo namaz chhod kar palat jaey. ho sakta hai ke wo anjaaney mein apney aap ko bad'duaa dey bethey."
163,"Hazrat Urwa bin Zuber sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai, unhoney kaha : main Marwan bin Hakam key paas gaya, chunanche hamney aapas mein un chizon ka zikr kiya jin sey wuzu wajib hota hai. Marwan ney kaha : Sharmgah ko chhuney sey bhi wuzu wajib ho jata hai. mainey kaha : mujhey to is baat ka ilm nahin. Marwan ney kaha : mujhey Hazrat Busraa binte Safwan (Raziallahu anha) ney bataya ke unhoney Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jab tum mein sey koi apni sharmgah (uzu) ko chhu bethey to usey chahiye ke wuzu karey."
164,"Hazrat Urwa bin Zuber sey manqul (naqal hui ) hai, unhoney kaha : Marwan ney Madiney ki Amaarat (governori) key doran mein zikr kiya ke jab aadmi apna haath uzu makhsus ko lagaey to usey uskey baad wuzu karna chahiye. mainey is ka inkar kiya aur kaha : jisney apney uzu makhsus ko haath lagaya is par koi wuzu nahin hai. to Marwan ney kaha ke mujhey Busraa binte Safwan (Raziallahu anha) ney bayan kiya ke unhoney Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko in chizon ka zikr kartey huye suna jin sey wuzu karna padta hai, chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : uzu makhsus ko chhuney sey bhi wuzu karey, Urwa ney kaha ke main Marwan sey behes karta raha yahan tak ke us ney apney muhafiz dastey sey eik aadmi bulaya aur usey Busraa key paas bheja. us ney un sey is riwayat key barey mein sawal kiya jo unhoney Marwan ko bayan ki thi to Hazrat Busraa (Raziallahu anha) ney wohi riwayat suna kar bheja jo Marwan ney mujhey unkey naam sey bayan ki thi."
165,Hazrat Talaq bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai unhoney kaha : hum wafad ki surat mein apney ilaqey sey nikley yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas pahunchey chunanche hamney aap ki baiat ki aur aap key sath namaz padhi. namaz khatam honey key baad eik badwi sa aadmi aaya aur kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! us aadmi key barey mein kya hukm hai jo namaz mein apney uzue-tanasul ko chhu bethta hai. aap ney farmaya : wo bhi terey jism ka eik tukda hi to hai.
166,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, farmati hain ke be-shak Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) namaz padhtey hotey aur main aap key samney is tarah leti hoti jaisey janaza hota hai yahan tak ke jab aap witr padhney ka irada farmatey to mujhey paaun laga kar jagaa detey."
167,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain : (yun samjho ke) tum mujhey dekh rahey ho ke main Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney leti hoti aur Allah key Rasool namaz padhtey hotey. jab aap sajda karney ka irada farmatey to mera paaun haath sey dabaatey main paaun suked leti phir aap sajda farmatey.
168,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke main Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney soi hoti thi aur merey paaun aap key qibley mein hotey they. jab aap sajda farmatey to merey paaun daba detey. main unhein suked leti. jab aap khadey hotey to phir bichha leti. un dino gharon mein chiragh nahin hotey they.
169,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke eik raat mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko apney sath na paya to mainey apney haathon sey aap ko talash karna shuru kar diya, chunanche mera haath aap key paaun ko laga jo sidhey khadey they, jab ke aap sajdey mein they aur padh rahey they : (أعوذ برضاک من سخطک … … … أنت کما أثنیت Ali (Raziallahu anhu) نفسک),''(aey Allah ! ) main terey ghussey sey ( bachney key liye) teri raza mandi aur teri saza sey ( bachney key liye) teri maafi ki panah hasil karta hun. aur terey ghazab sey ( bachney key liye) teri rehmat ki panah mein aata hun. main teri puri tareef nahin kar sakta. to isi tarah hai jis tarah tu ney khud apni tareef ki hai.''"
170,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apni baaz biwiyon ko bosa detey phir namaz padhtey aur naya wuzu na farmatey they. Imaam abu-Abdur-Rehman Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke is masley mein is sey behtar koi riwayat nahin agar-che uski sanad mursal (munqata) hai (kyonkey Ibrahim Taimi ka Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey samaa (sun'na) sabit nahin hai). Aa'mash ney is hadees ko Habib bin Abi Sabit an Aaisha ki sanad sey bayan kiya hai. Yahya bin Saeed Qataan (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke ye riwayat aur isi sanad (Habeeb an Urwa an Aaisha) sey manqul (naqal hui) eik aur riwayat : istihaza wali aurat namaz padhti rahey agar-che khoon chataai par girta ho. dono ghair moatabar hain.
171,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : aag par paki hui chiz khaney sey wuzu karo."
172,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huye suna : aag par paki hui chiz (khaney) sey wuzu karo."
173,"Abdullah bin Ibrahim bin Qaariz kehtey hain ke mainey Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko masjid ki chhat par wuzu kartey dekha, unhoney farmaya : mainey paneer key tukdey khaye they, is liye mainey wuzu kiya kyonkey mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko aag par paki hui chiz (khaney) sey wuzu karney ka hukm detey suna hai."
174,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke kya main us khaney ki wajeh sey wuzu karun jisey main Allah ki kitab mein halal paata hun sirf is bina par ke wo aag par pakka hai? Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney bahut si kankariyaan jama kin aur farmaya : main in kankariyon ki tadaad key barabar gawahi deta hun ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aag par paki hui chiz (khaney) sey wuzu karo.
175,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aag par paki hui chiz (khaney) sey wuzu karo."
176,"Hazrat Abu-Ayyub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aag par paki hui chiz (khaney) sey wuzu karo."
177,"Hazrat Abu-Talha Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aag par paki hui chiz (khaney) sey wuzu karo."
178,"Hazrat Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har us chiz (key khaney) sey wuzu karo jisey aag ney pakaayaa ho."
179,Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huye suna : har us chiz (key khaney) sey wuzu karo jisey aag ney pakaayaa ho.
180,Abu-Sufiyaan bin Saeed bin Akhnas bin Shuraiq Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki biwi mohtarma Hazrat Umme Habiba (Raziallahu anha) key paas gaey. Umme Habiba (Raziallahu anha) un ki khaala thin. unhoney in ko sattu pilaey phir farmaya : aey bhaanjey ! wuzu karo kyonkey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har us chiz (key khaney) sey wuzu karo jisey aag ney pakaayaa ho.
181,"Abu-Sufiyaan bin Saeed bin Akhnas sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki biwi mohtarma Hazrat Umme Habiba (Raziallahu anha) ney us sey kaha, jab ke us ney sattu piye they : aey bhaanjey ! wuzu kar kyonkey mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huye suna : aag par paki hui chiz (khaney) sey wuzu karo."
182,Hazrat Umme Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kandhey ka gosht khaya  phir aap key paas Bilal aaye to aap namaz key liye tashrif ley gaey aur pani ko chhua tak nahin.
183,"Hazrat Umme Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ( kabhi kabhi ) subah key waqt ehtilaam (sawapan dosh) nahin balke jima (sanbhog) sey junbi (naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan) hotey they, phir (isi tarah) roza rakh letey they. aur is hadees key sath unhoney hamein ye hadees bhi bayan ki ke eik dafa unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko pehlu ka bhuna huwa gosht pesh kiya, aap ney is mein sey kuchh khaya phir namaz key liye uth khadey huye aur wuzu nahin farmaya."
184,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke mainey dekha ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney roti aur gosht khaya phir namaz key liye uth khadey huye aur wuzu nahin farmaya.
185,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke un do kamon mein sey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka aakhiri kaam ye tha ke aap aag par paki hui chiz (khaney) sey wuzu nahin farmatey they.
186,"Hazrat Suwed bin Noman (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke wo (Suwed) ghazwae-khaibar key saal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath nikley yahan tak ke jab lashkar sehbaa mein pahuncha aur wo khaibar sey qarib tareen ilaaqa hai, to aap ney Asr ki namaz padhaai phir aap ney apna apna zaade-raah laney ka hukm diya to sirf sattu hi laye gaey, aap ney hukm diya to sattu pani mein bhigoey gaey, phir aap ney khaye aur hamney bhi khaye phir aap Maghrib ki namaz key liye uth khadey huye. aap ney sirf kulli ki aur hamney bhi kulli hi ki, phir aap ney namaz padhaai aur wuzu nahin kiya."
187,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney doodh piya, phir pani mangwaya aur kulli ki, phir aap ney farmaya : tehqiq is mein chiknaahat hoti hai."
188,Hazrat Qais bin Aasim sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke wo musalman huye to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein hukm diya ke pani aur beeri key patton sey ghusl karen.
189,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Samaama bin Assaal Hanfi (Raziallahu anhu) masjid sey qarib eik jama shuda pani ki taraf gaey aur ghusl kiya, phir masjid mein dakhil huye aur kaha :(أشھد أن لا الہ الا اللہ … … … عبدہ ورسولہ), 'main gawahi deta hun ke Allah Taala key siwa koi (sachcha) mabood nahin, wo yaktaa hai, us ka koi shareek nahin aur Muhammad(Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur Rasool hain.'' aey Muhammad ! Allah ki qism ! is sey pehley roey-zameen par koi chehra aap key chehrey sey badh kar mujhey napasand nahin tha magar ab aap ka chehra tamam chehron sey mujhey mehbub tareen ho gaya hai, isi ke saath aap key sawar mujhey pakad laye hain jabkey main Umerey key iraday sey ja raha tha. ab aap ka kya farman hai? aap ney usey (mubarak baad aur) khush-khabri di aur usey Umra karney ka hukm diya. ye riwayat mukhtasar hai."
190,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas gaya aur kaha : Abu Talib faut ho gaey hain. aap ney farmaya : jaao usey daba aao Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : bilashuba wo mushrik faut huye hain. aap ney farmaya : jaao usey daba-aao jab mainey unhein daba diya to main aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas wapis aaya. aap ney mujh sey farmaya : ghusl karo.
191,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab aadmi aurat ki chaar shaakhon (haath paaun) key darmiyan beth kar koshish karey to ghusl wajib ho gaya."
192,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab aadmi aurat ki chaar shaakhon ( haath paaun ) key darmiyan bethey, phir koshish karey to ghusl wajib ho gaya. Imaam Abu Abdur-Rehman Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke ye sanad ghalat hai. sahih sanad yun hai : ( أشعث an الحسن an أبی ھریرۃ ) Nazar bin Shumail waghera ney is hadees ko Shoba sey isi tarah bayan kiya hai jis tarah Khalid ney bayan kiya hai."
193,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke mujhey mazi bahut ziyada aati thi to mujh sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mazi dekho to apney uzu ( waghera ) ko dho lo aur namaz wala wuzu karo lekin jab tum zor sey mani nikalo to ghusl karo.
194,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mujhey mazi bahut ziyada aati thi, chunanche mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha to aap ney farmaya : jab tum mazi dekho to apney uzu ko dho kar wuzu kar lo aur jab tum zor sey mani nikalo to ghusl kar lo."
195,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Ummey Sulaim (Raziallahu anha) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey aurat key barey mein puchha jo khuwab mein wohi kuchh dekhti hai jo mard dekhta hai to aap ney farmaya : jab wo pani nikaley to ghusl karey.
196,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Hazrat Ummey Sulaim (Raziallahu anha) ney Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey baat cheet ki. Hazrat Aaisha bhi paas bethi hui thin. unhoney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! Allah Taala haq baat sey nahin sharmata. aap bataeyn agar koi aurat neend mein wo kuchh dekhti hai jo mard dekhta hai to kya wo ghusl kerey? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haan. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney kaha : afsos tujh par ! kya aurat bhi ye kuchh dekhti hai? to Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) meri taraf mutawajjeh huye aur farmaya : terey haath khaak aalud hon (bachchey mein aurat ki) mushaabihat kaisey hoti hai?
197,"Hazrat Ummey Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke eik aurat ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! Allah Taala haq baat sey nahin sharmata kya aurat par ghusl wajib hai jab usey ehtilaam (sawapndosh) ho jaey? aap ney farmaya : han, jab wo pani (mani) dekhey. Hazrat Ummey Salma (Raziallahu anha) hansney lagin aur kehney lagin : kya aurat ko bhi ehtilaam hota hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to kis wajeh sey bachcha aurat key mushabeh hota hai?"
198,Hazrat Khaula binte Hakim (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey us aurat key barey mein puchha jisey neend mein ehtilaam (sawapndosh) ho jata hai. aap ney farmaya : jab wo pani (mani) dekhey to ghusl karey.
199,"Hazrat Abu-Ayyub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : pani (ghusl) pani (mani) sey wajib hota hai."
200,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mard ki mani ghaadi safed aur aurat ki mani patli aur zard hoti hai. un dono mein sey jo ghalib aa jaey, usi sey (bachchey ki) mushaabihat hoti hai."
201,Hazrat Fatima binte Qais (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aayin aur bataya ke mujhey istihaaza  (be-qaaeda khoon) aata hai. unhoney bataya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : ye to eik rag (ka khoon) hai. jab tujhey haiz ka khoon aaye to namaz chhod dey aur jab haiz aana band ho jaey to nahaa dho kar namaz shuru kar dey (khuwah istihazey ka khoon aa hi raha ho).
202,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab haiz ka khoon aana shuru ho jaey to namaz (waghera) chhod do aur jab khoon aana ruk jaey to ghusl karo."
203,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Ummey Habiba binte Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ko saat saal istihaza (be-qaaeda khoon) aata raha. unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey is baat ki shikayat ki to aap ney farmaya, ye haiz nahin balke ye to eik rag (ka khoon) hai, lihaza (haiz khatam honey key baad) nahaa dho kar namaz waghera padhti raho (khuwah istihazey ka khoon aata rahey)."
204,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi aur Zainab binte Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ki behan Umme Habiba (Raziallahu anha) ko istihaza (be-qaaeda khoon) aata tha to unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey ye masla puchha chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye (be-qaaeda khoon) haiz nahin hai balke ye to eik rag (ka khoon hai). jab tujhey haiz ka (be-qaeeda) khoon aana ruk jaey to nahaa-dho kar namaz padha kar aur jab haiz ka khoon aana shuru ho jaey to namaz chhod diya kar. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke wo har namaz key liye ghusl kar key namaz padhti thin. kabhi kabhi wo apni behan Zainab binte Jahash  jo ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key nikah mein thin key hujrey mein tab mein ghusl kartin to (istihaazey key) khoon ki surkhi pani key rang par ghalib aa jati. wo jaatin (masjid mein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key peechhey namaz padhtin. ye (istihaazey key khoon ka aana) unhein namaz sey na rokta tha.
205,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Ummey Habiba (Raziallahu anha) jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki saali aur Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi thin wo saat saal tak istihaza mein mubtala rahin. unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey uski baabat puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye haiz ka khoon nahin balke ye to kisi rag ka khoon hai. tum (haiz khatam honey par) ghusl kar liya karo aur namaz padha karo (khuwah istihaza jari rahey).
206,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Ummey Habiba binte Jahash ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey masla puchha aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey (khoon) istihaza aata hai. aap ney farmaya : ye to eik rag (ka khoon) hai. tum (haiz key ikhtitaam par) ghusl karo aur namaz padho. to wo har namaz key liye ghusl kar liya karti thin.
207,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Ummey Habiba (Raziallahu anha) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey khoon (istihaaza) key barey mein sawal kiya. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya ke mainey unka tab khoon sey bhara huwa dekha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey farmaya : tum itney arsey tak (namaz waghera sey) ruki raho jitney arsey tak tumhein haiz aaya karta tha, phir ghusl kar lo (khuwah khoon istihaza jari ho)."
208,"Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) farmatey hain, hamein ye hadees (Qutaiba) ney eik baar phir bayan farmaai to (Yazeed bin Abi Habeeb aur Iraak bin Malik key darmiyan) Ja'far bin Rabeea'a ka zikr nahin kiya."
209,"Hazrat Ummey Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daur main eik aurat ko kasrat sey (khoon) istihaaza aaya karta tha to Hazrat Ummey Salma (Raziallahu anha) ney uskey liye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey masla puchha to aap ney farmaya : wo un dino ko yad karey jin mein usey bimari lagney sey pehley haiz aaya karta tha to mahiney mein sey itney din wo namaz chhodey rakhey. jab wo din guzar jaeyn to wo ghusl kar ley, phir langot baandh ley aur namaz padhni shuru kar dey."
210,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Ummey Habiba binte Jahash jo Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anha) key nikah mein thin unhein istihazey ki takleef ho gaee aur wo kabhi khoon sey paak nahin hoti thin. un ki ye haalat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney zikr ki gaee to aap ney farmaya : ye haiz nahin balke (shetan ki taraf sey) reham main eik kachoka hai, lihaza wo apney haiz ki wo miqdaar yad karey jis mein usey haiz aaya karta tha, chunanche us doran mein wo namaz chhod dey, phir us (haiz guzar janey) key baad wo har namaz key liye ghusl karey."
211,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Hazrat Umme-Habiba binte Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ko saat saal tak istihaza jari raha to unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha. aap ney farmaya : ye haiz nahin balke ye to eik rag (ka khoon ) hai to aap ney unhein hukm diya ke apney haiz key waqt namaz waghera chhod den, phir ( haiz guzar janey key baad ) wo ghusl keren, aur namaz padhen chunanche Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) har namaz key waqt ghusl karti thin."
212,Hazrat Fatima binte Abi Habish (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aayin aur khoon ki shikayat ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye to eik rag (ka khoon ) hai. tum khayal rakhna jab tumharey haiz key din aa jaeyn to namaz na padho aur jab guzar jaeyn to naha dho kar aainda haiz tak namaz padho. ye hadees daleel hai ke (قرء ) sey murad haiz hai. Imaam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke is hadees ko Hazrat Urwa sey Hisham bin Urwa ney bhi bayan kiya hai lekin unhoney wo alfaz zikr nahin kiye jo Munzir ney zikr kiye hain.
213,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Fatima binte Abi Habish (Raziallahu anha) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aayin aur kehney lagin : tehqiq mujhey istihaza (be-qaaeda khoon kasrat sey aata) hai, main kabhi khoon sey paak nahin hoti to kya main namaz chodey rakhun? aap ney farmaya : nahin  ye to eik rag (ka khoon) hai, ye haiz nahin. jab tumhein haiz ka khoon aaye to namaz chhod do aur jab haiz ka khoon band ho jaey to naha dho kar namaz shuru kar do."
214,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai ke eik aurat ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein istihaza ( be qaaeda khoon aata ) tha. usey kaha gaya : tehqiq ye eik sarkash rag hai. aur usey hukm diya gaya ke Zohar ko muakhkhar (deri) karey aur Asr ko muqaddam karey aur un dono key liye eik ghusl kerey. isi tarah Maghrib ko muakhkhar karey aur Isha ko jaldi padhey aur dono key liye eik ghusl karey aur subah ki namaz key liye eik ghusl karey.
215,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anha) sey Hazrat Asma binte Umes key waqiye key barey mein riwayat hai ke Zul-haleefa mein jab un key yahaan bachcha paida huwa to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : unhein kaho ke ghusl kar key ehraam baandhen.
216,"Hazrat Faatima binte Abi Habeesh (Raziallahu anha) ney kaha ke mujhey istihaazey ka khoon aata tha to mujh sey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab haiz ka khoon aa raha ho aur ye siyahi maael khoon hota hai jo pehchana jata hai, to namaz sey ruk jaao aur jab doosra khoon (istihaazey ka) ho to wuzu kar key namaz padha karo ye to rag (ka khoon) hai."
217,"Muhammad bin Musannaa ney kaha, hamein ye riwayat (216) ibne Abi Adi ney apni kitab sey bayan ki aur (mindarjazail (neechey likhi)) riwayat (217) apney hifz sey bayan ki. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Faatima binte Abi Habeesh (Raziallahu anha) ko istihaza aata tha to unhein Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haiz ka khoon siyah hota hai jo pehchana jata hai. jab ye khoon aaye to namaz sey ruk jaao aur jab doosra khoon ho to (har namaz key liye) wuzu karo aur namaz padho. Imaam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke is hadees ko bahut sey raawiyon ney bayan kiya hai, lekin kisi ney wo alfaz zikr nahin kiye jo ibne Abi Adi ney zikr kiye hain (واللہ تعالیٰ أعلم)."
218,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Faatima binte Abi Habeesh ko istihaza aata tha. unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha : aey Allah key Rasool ! istihaazey key marz mein mubtala hun main kabhi paak nahin hoti to kya namaz chhod dun? aap ney farmaya : ye to rag (ka khoon) hai, haiz nahin. jab haiz aaney lagey to namaz chhod diya karo aur jab wo ruk jaey to khoon key asraat dho lo (ghusl karo) aur (namaz key liye) wuzu karo kyonkey ye rag (ka khoon) hai, haiz nahin. raawi sey kaha gaya : (haiz key ikhtitaam par) ghusl ho ga? to us ney kaha : is main to koi shak hi nahin kar sakta. Imaam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke main nahin janta ke Hammad bin Zaid key ilawa kisi raawi ney is hadees mein (وتوضئی) wuzu karo. key alfaz zikr kiye hon. jabkey is hadees ko Hisham bin Urwa sey bahut sey raawiyon ney bayan kiya hai magar kisi ney ye lafz zikr nahin kiya."
219,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Faatima binte Abi Habeesh ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main kabhi khoon sey paak nahin hoti to kya namaz chhod hi dun? aap ney farmaya : ye to rag (ka khoon) hai, haiz (ka) nahin hai, lihaza jab haiz aana shuru ho to namaz chhod do phir jab haiz key din guzar jaeyn to khoon key asraat dho lo yani ghusl karo aur namaz shuru kar do."
220,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Faatima binte Abi Habeesh ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main kabhi paak nahin hoti to kya bilkul namaz chhod dun? aap ney farmaya : nahin ye to eik rag (ka khoon) hai, haiz nahin hai, lihaza jab haiz ka khoon aaney lagey to namaz chhod do aur jab khatam ho jaey to khoon key aasaar dho kar (ghusl kar key) namaz shuru kar do."
221,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey jab koi shakhs junbi ho to thehrey huye pani mein ghusl na kerey.
222,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi thehrey huye pani mein hergiz peshab na karey ke phir is mein ghusl kerega."
223,Hazrat Ghuzef bin Haris sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) raat key kis hissey mein ghusl farmaya kartey they? unhoney farmaya : aap kabhi raat key shuru mein ghusl farmatey aur kabhi aakhir mein. mainey kaha : har tareef Allah ki jisney us mamley mein wusat rakhi.
224,"Ghuzef bin Haris bayan kartey hain ke main Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key paas gaya aur un sey puchha ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) raat key shuru mein ghusl farmaya kartey they ya raat key aakhir mein? Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : dono waqt, kabhi raat key shuru hi mein ghusl farma letey aur kabhi aakhir raat ko ghusl farmatey. mainey kaha : har tareef Allah ki jisney us mamley mein wusat rakhi hai."
225,Hazrat Abu-Samah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat kya karta tha. jab aap ghusl ka irada farmatey to mujh sey farmatey : meri taraf apni peeth kar lo. main aap ki taraf peeth kar leta. is tarah mein aap ko parda bhi kar deta.
226,Hazrat Umme-Hani (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke main fateh Makka key din Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas gaee to mainey aap ko ghusl kartey paya jab ke Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ney aap ko eik kapdey sey parda kar rakha tha. mainey salam kaha to aap ney farmaya : kon? mainey kaha : Umme-Haani ! jab aap ghusl sey farigh huye to aap ney eik kapdey mein aath rakaat padhein jab ke wo (kapda) aap ney kandhon par lapet rakha tha.
227,Musa Johni sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Mujahid key paas eik piyala laya gaya. merey andazey key mutabiq wo aath ratl tha. Mujahid kehney lagey ke mujh sey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney bayan kya : beshak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) itney pani sey ghusl farma liya kartey they.
228,"Hazrat abu-Salma sey riwayat hai ke main aur Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ka razaaii bhai Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key paas gaey, chunanche Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key bhai ney un sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key ghusl key barey mein sawal kya to unhoney eik bartan mangwaya jis main eik saa pani tha, phir unhoney parda latkaya aur ghusl farmaya aur apney sar par teen dafa pani dala."
229,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik piyaley sey ghusl farma liya kartey they jo eik farq key barabar tha, isi ke sath main aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (eik waqt) eik bartan mein ghusl kar liya kartey they."
230,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik mudd sey wuzu aur paanch mudd sey ghusl farma liya kartey they.
231,"Hazrat Abu-Jafar (Muhammad Baaqar) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) kehtey hain ke hamara Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) key paas ghusl key barey mein ikhtilaf ho gaya. Hazrat Jabir farmaney lagey : ghusle-janabat (sambhog ke bad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan ka ghusl) key liye eik saa pani kafi hai. hamney kaha : eik do saa to kafi nahin ho saktey. Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey us shakhsiyat ko to eik saa kafi tha jo tum sey behtar aur tum sey ziyada baalon waley they, yani Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam)."
232,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke main aur Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik bartan sey ghusl kya kartey they jo taqriban eik « farq » key barabar hota tha.
233,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur main eik bartan sey ghusl kar liya kartey they. hum b-yak waqt us sey chalo bhartey they.
234,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke tehqiq mein aur Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ( b-yak waqt eik bartan sey ghusle-janabat kar liya kartey they.
235,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mainey apney aap ko dekha, mein aur Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ghusl kartey waqt bartan apni apni taraf khinchtey they."
236,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke main aur Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik bartan sey ghusl kar liya kartey they.
237,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain ke mujhey meri khala, ummul-Mominin Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ney bataya ke beshak wo aur Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik hi bartan sey ghusl kar liya kartey they."
238,"ummul-Mominin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey puchha gaya : kya aurat ( biwi ) mard key sath ghusl kar sakti hai? unhoney farmaya : han, jab wo samajhdar ho. mainey apney aap ko dekha ke main aur Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik tab sey ghusl kar liya kartey they. pehley hum apney haathon par pani baha kar unhein achi tarah saaf kar letey, phir apney baqi jism par pani bahatey, Aaraj raawi ney kaha : aurat sharmgah ki taraf tawajjoh dey, na himaqat sey kaam ley."
239,"Humed bin Abdur-Rehman bayan kartey hain ke main eik aisey aadmi sey mila jo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath raha hai, jis tarah Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) chaar saal tak Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath rahey hain. us ney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mana farmaya ke koi aadmi har roz kanghi karey ya apney ghusl khaney mein peshab karey ya mard aurat key bachey huye pani sey aur aurat mard key bachey huye pani sey ghusl karey balke dono ikhattey chullu bharen ."
240,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke main aur Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik bartan sey ghusl kartey they. mein aap sey jaldi ( ghusl ) karney ki koshish karti aur aap mujh sey jaldi kartey yahan tak ke aap farmatey : merey liye pani rehney do. aur main kehti : aap merey liye pani chhod den. ( Hadees key raawi ) Suwed ney ( yun ) kaha : aap mujh sey jaldi kartey aur main aap sey jaldi karti, chunanche mein kehti : aap merey liye (pani ) chhod den. aap merey liye (pani ) chhod den."
241,Hazrat Umme-Hani (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ney aisey piyaley sey ghusl kya jis mein gundhey huye aatey ka asar ( nishan ) tha.
242,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki biwi mohtarma Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey guzarish ki ke aey Allah key Rasool ! main apney sar ki mendhiyaan mazbooti sey baandhti hun to kya ghusle-janabat (sambhog ke bad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan ka ghusl) key waqt inhein kholun? aap ney farmaya : tumhein itna kafi hai ke apney sar par pani key teen chullu dal liya karo phir apney sarey jism par pani baha lo."
243,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke hum Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Hajjatul-wadaa key saal nikley. mainey Umrey ka ehraam baandha chunanche main Makka aai to haiz ki haalat mein thi, lihaza main Baitullah ka tawaf kar saki na Safa, Marwa ki saee. mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey is ki shikayat ki. aap ney farmaya, 'sar key baal khol lo. (ghusl kar key) kanghi kar lo aur Haj ka ehraam baandh lo lekin Umra chhod do. mainey isi tarah kiya. jab hamney Haj mukammal kar liya to aap ney mujhey (merey bhai) Abdur-Rehman bin Abu-Bakar Raziallahu Anhuma key sath Tan'eem ki taraf bheja to mainey Umra kiya. aap ney farmaya : ye tumharey (us) Umrey ki jagah hai. imaam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke ye hadees (مالک an ھشام بن عروہ) ki sanad sey gharib hai kyonkey Ash'hab key siwa kisi ney usey (is tarah ) bayan nahin kiya."
244,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab ghusle-janabat farmatey to aap key liye bartan rakha jata, aap haathon ko bartan mein dalney sey pehley un par pani bahatey, jab haath dho letey to phir apna daayan haath bartan mein daltey, phir daeyn sey pani daltey aur baain sey apni sharmgah dhotey. jab us sey farigh hotey to daeyn haath sey baain par pani dal kar dono haathon ko dhotey, phir teen dafa kulli kartey aur naak mein pani chadhatey, phir apney sar par teen dafa dono haath bhar kar pani daltey, phir ( baqi ) jism par bahatey."
245,"Hazrat Abu-Salma sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key ghusle-janabat (sambhog ke bad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan ka ghusl) key barey mein puchha to unhoney bataya ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apney haathon par teen dafa pani daltey, phir apni sharmgah dhotey, phir apney haath dhotey, phir kulli kartey aur naak mein pani chadha kar naak ko saaf kartey phir apney sar par teen dafa pani daltey, phir apney baqi jism par pani bahatey."
246,"Hazrat abu-Salma sey riwayat hai ke main Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key paas gaya aur un sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key ghusle-janabat key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas bartan laya jata, aap apney dono haathon par teen dafa pani bahatey, phir unhein dhotey, phir apney daeyn haath sey apney baain haath par pani daltey aur apni sharmgah aur raanon par jo kuch hota usey dhotey, phir apney haath dhotey, phir kulli kartey aur naak mein pani chadha kar naak ko khub achi tarah saaf kartey, phir apney sar par teen dafa pani daltey, phir baqi sarey jism par pani bahatey."
247,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka ghusl-janabat (sambhog ke bad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan ka ghusl) bayan farmaya, kaha : aap apney haathon ko teen dafa dhotey, phir apney daeyn haath sey baain par teen dafa pani dal kar apni sharmgah aur dusri lagi hui ratoobat (gandagi) dhotey, (Hadees key raawi) umr bin Ubaid kehtey hain ke merey ilm key mutabiq unhon (Ustad) ney yehi kaha, phir apney daeyn haath sey baain par teen dafa pani daltey, phir teen dafa kulli farmatey aur teen dafa naak mein pani chadha kar usey saaf kartey, phir apna chehra aur dono bazu teen dafa dhotey, phir apney sar par teen dafa pani bahatey, phir apney (sarey jism) par pani bahatey."
248,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab ghusle-janabat (sambhog ke bad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan ka ghusl) farmatey to sab sey pehley apney haath dhotey, phir wuzu farmatey jis tarah namaz key liye wuzu farmaya kartey they, phir apni ungliyan pani mein daltey aur un sey baalon ki jadon mein Khilal kartey, phir apney sar par teen chullu pani daltey, phir apney sarey jism par pani bahatey."
249,"Hazrat Urwa bayan kartey hain ke mujhey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key ghusle-janabat ki babat bayan kya ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ( sab sey pehley) apney haath dhotey they aur wuzu farmatey aur apney sar key baalon mein ( geeli ) ungliyan phertey they, ( yahan tak ke baal geeley ho jatey ) phir apney sarey jism par pani bahatey,"
250,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ( pehley) apney sar key baalon ko Khilal sey achi tarah tar kar letey they, phir sar par teen chalo (pani ) daltey ."
251,"Hazrat Juber bin mut'im (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke kuch logon ney Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ghusl key barey mein ikhtilaf kya. kisi ney kaha ke main to itni itni dafa ( sar ko) dhota hun, chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main to apney sar par sirf teen chalo pani bahaataa hun."
252,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai ke eik aurat ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey ghusl haiz key barey mein puchha to aap ney usey bataya ke kaisey ghusl kerey. phir farmaya : kastoori laga huwa rui ka eik tukda ley lo aur us sey safai kar lo. us ney kaha : is sey kaisey safai karun? aap ney apna chehra dhanp liya aur farmaya : « subhan Allah » tum uskey sath safai kar lo. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney kaha : mainey us aurat ko apni taraf khincha aur kaha ke usey khoon key nishaanaat par laga lo.
253,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ghusl key baad wuzu nahin farmatey they.
254,"ummul-Mominin Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) bayan farmati hain ke mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key ghusle-janabat key liye pani qarib kya. aap ney apni hatheliyon ko do ya teen baar dhoya, phir apna daayan haath bartan mein dakhil kya aur us sey apni sharmgah par pani dala, phir usey baain haath sey dhoya, phir baayan haath zamin par maara aur usey zor sey ragda, phir namaz wala wuzu kya, phir apney sar par dono haath bhar-bhar kar teen dafa pani dala, phir apney baqi ( sarey ) jism ko dhoya, phir us jagah sey eik taraf hat kar apney paaun dhoey, phir main aap key paas rumaal laee to aap ney wapis kar diya."
255,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ghusl farmaya aur baad mein rumaal laya gaya to aap ney usey qubul na farmaya balke pani ko haathon key sath is tarah jhaadney lagey.
256,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan farmati hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur Amr ney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab janabat (sambhog ke bad naapaaki) ki haalat mein khaney ya soney ka irada farmatey to wuzu farma letey. Amr ney apni hadees mein ye lafz ziyada bayan kiye ke namaz wala wuzu farma letey they.
257,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab janabat ki haalat mein soney ka irada kartey to wuzu farmatey aur jab khaney ka irada kartey to haath dho letey.
258,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab janabat ki haalat mein soney ka irada farmatey to wuzu farmatey aur jab khaney ya peeney ka irada farmatey to apney haath dhotey, phir khatey peetey ."
259,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke beshak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab soney ka irada farmatey aur junbi hotey to soney sey pehley namaz wala wuzu farma letey they.
260,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney guzarish ki ke aey Allah key Rasool ! kya hum mein sey koi janabat (sambhog ke bad naapaaki) ki haalat mein sau sakta hai? aap ney farmaya : ba-sharte ke wuzu kar ley.
261,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney zikr kiya ke (kabhi) mein raat ko junbi (sambhog ke bad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan) ho jata hun (to kya karun)? aap ney farmaya : apni sharmgah dho lo, wuzu kar lo, phir so jaao."
262,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is ghar mein ( rehmat key) farishtey dakhil nahin hotey jis mein tasweer, kutta ya junbi ho."
263,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi dobara jima karna chahey to wuzu kar ley."
264,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasool akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik raat mein apni tamam biwiyon key paas eik hi ghusl key sath gaey.
265,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik hi ghusl key sath apni tamam biwiyon key paas chaley jatey they."
266,Hazrat Abdullah bin Salma bayan kartey hain ke main aur do aadmi Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaye to unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) baitul-khala sey bahar tashrif latey to Quran Majeed padhtey. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamarey sath gosht khatey aur aap ko Quran Majeed padhney sey janabat (sambhog ke bad naapaaki ki haalat) key siwa koi chiz rukawat na hoti thi.
267,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) janabat key ilawa har haal mein Quran Majeed padh liya kartey they.
268,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab apney kisi sahabi ko miltey they to ( musaafhey key baad ) usey haath phertey aur usey dua detey. eik din subh key waqt mainey aap ko dekha to mainey rukh badal liya, phir jab din ooncha ho gaya to main aap key paas aaya. aap ney farmaya : mainey tumhein dekha tha, lekin tum ney rukh badal liya tha. mainey kaha : tehqiq mein junbi tha. mujhey khatra tha ke aap mujhey haath lagaeyngey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tehqiq musalman paleed nahin hota."
269,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) mujhey miley jab ke main junbi tha. aap ( mulaqat key liye) meri taraf maael huye. mainey kaha : main junbi hun. aap ney farmaya : tehqiq musalman napak nahin hota."
270,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) unhein Madina Munawra key eik raastey mein miley. jab ke wo ( Abu-Hurera ) junbi they, isliye wo aap sey khisak gaey aur ghusl kya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein na paya. phir jab wo aaye to aap ney farmaya : Abu-Hurera ! tum kahan they? mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! jab aap mujhey miley they to main junbi tha. mainey us haal mein aap key sath bethna pasand na kya yahan tak ke ghusl kar lun. aap ney farmaya : « subhan Allah! » tehqiq momin paleed nahin hota."
271,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke eik dafa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) masjid mein they ke aap ney farmaya : aey Aaisha ! mujhey kapda pakdao . unhoney kaha : main namaz nahin padhti (mein haiz sey hun.) aap ney farmaya : beshak wo ( haiz ) tumharey haath mein nahin. to unhoney kapda pakda diya.
272,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey masjid sey chataai pakda do. mainey kaha : main haalat haiz mein hun to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumhara haiz tumharey haath mein nahin hai.
273,"(Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) kehtey hain :) hamen Is-haq bin Ibrahim ney bayan kya, unhoney kaha : hamen abu-Muaawia ney Aamash sey usi sanad key sath aisi hi riwayat bayan ki."
274,"Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) azwaj (jodey) mutahrat mein sey kisi ki god mein sar rakhtey aur Quran Majeed ki tilawat farmatey, halanke wo haiz sey hoti thi. isi tarah hum mein sey koi chataaii ley kar masjid mein bicha deti thi, halanke wo haaiza hoti thi."
275,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka sar mubarak hum (azwaje-mutahrat) mein sey kisi eik ki god mein hota tha jab ke wo haiz ki haalat mein hoti thi aur aap Quran Majeed tilawat farmatey they.
276,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aetikaf ki haalat mein apna sar merey qarib kar detey, mein usey dho deti, halanke mein haiz ki haalat mein hoti thi."
277,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aetikaf ki haalat mein apna sar mubarak masjid sey bahar meri taraf nikal detey aur main usey dho deti thi, halanke mein haiz ki haalat mein hoti thi."
278,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke main Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sar mubarak ko kanghi kar diya karti thi, halanke mein haiz ki haalat mein hoti thi."
279,« Quteba » bin Saeed ney Imam Malik ki sanad sey aisi hi hadees bayan ki hai magar us hadees mein Malik key Ustad Hisham bin Urwa key bajaey Zohri hain. us riwayat mein « Quteba » key sath Ali bin Shuaib bhi un ki muwaafiqat kartey hain.
280,"Hazrat Shureh sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey puchha : kya aurat haiz ki haalat mein apney khawind key sath kha pi sakti hai? unhoney farmaya : haan. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) mujhey bulatey they to main aap key sath khana khati jab ke main haiz ki haalat mein hoti thi. aap gosht wali haddi pakadtey aur mujhey qism detey ke main pehley shuru karun. main us sey kuch gosht nochti, phir main haddi rakh deti, phir aap usey pakadtey aur us sey nochna shuru farma detey. apna munh mubarak usi jagah rakhtey jahan mainey munh rakha hota tha. isi tarah aap pani mangwatay aur peeney sey pehley mujhey qism detey ke main shuru karun. main pani pakadti aur kuch pani peeti, phir rakh deti to aap pakadtey aur peena shuru farma detey. aur apna munh mubarak piyaley ki usi jagah rakhtey jahan mainey apna munh rakha hota tha."
281,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apna munh mubarak us jagah rakhtey jahan sey mainey piya hota tha, phir mujh sey bacha huwa pani nosh farmatey halanke mein haiz ki haalat mein hoti thi."
282,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) mujhey bartan pakdatey, chunanche mein us sey peeti, halanke mein haiz ki haalat mein hoti thi, phir main bartan aap ko dey deti to aap qasdan merey munh wali jagah par munh mubarak rakhtey."
283,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main haiz ki haalat mein pani peeti, phir main bartan Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko pakda deti. aap merey munh wali jagah par apna munh mubarak rakh kar nosh farmatey. mein haddi sey gosht nochti jab ke main haiz sey hoti thi aur main wo haddi aap ko pakda deti to aap merey munh wali jagah par apna munh mubarak rakhtey."
284,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke eik dafa mein Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath eik chadar mein leti hui thi ke mujhey haiz shuru ho gaya, chunanche mein aahisatagi sey uthi aur apney haiz waley kapdey pehan liye. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tumhein haiz shuru ho gaya hai? mainey kaha : ji haan. aap ney mujhey bulaya aur main aap key sath usi chadar mein let gaee."
285,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik hi chadar mein raat guzartey they, halanke main haiz sey hoti thi, chunanche agar aap ko mujh sey kuch (khoon lag jata to aap sirf itni jagah dho letey, zayed na dhotey aur us kapdey mein namaz padhtey, phir ( dobara merey sath ) let jatey, chunanche agar kuch ( khoon) mujh sey aap key kapdon ko lag jata to isi tarah kartey, ( sirf itni jagah dhotey ) us sey zayed na dhotey aur us kapdey mein namaz padh letey."
286,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hum ( azwaje-mutahrat ) main sey kisi ko jab wo haaiza hoti, hukm detey they ke wo apna izaar baandh ley, phir aap uskey sath let jatey they."
287,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke hum ( azwaj (jodey) mutahraat ) main sey kisi ko haiz shuru hota to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) usey hukm detey they ke wo izaar baandh ley, phir aap uskey sath let jatey they."
288,"ummul-Mominin Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apni aurton mein sey kisi key sath let jaya kartey they jab ke wo haiz sey hoti thi, b-sharte-ke us ney kamar par aisa izaar baandh rakha hota jo nisf raanon ya ghutnon tak pahunchta. Leis ki hadees mein hai : wo izaar baandhey hoti."
289,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Yahudi qom mein jab kisi aurat ko haiz shuru hota to wo uskey sath mil jal kar khatey na peetey they aur na ghar mein uskey sath rehtey. sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey us barey mein puchha to Allah Taala ney ye aayat utaar di : ( ویسئلونک an المحیض , قل ھو اذی … … ) ye aap sey haiz key barey mein poochhtey hain, aap farma dijiye : wo gandi chiz hai … … … padhi. to Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein hukm diya ke wo unkey sath mil jal kar khaeyn piyen aur gharon mein unkey sath rahen aur unkey sath har qism ki mohabbat piyaar keren, siwaye jima key (ke wo haram hai.) Yahudi kehney lagey : ye Rasool hamari har chiz mein mukhalifat karta hai to Usaid bin Huzer aur Ibad bin Bishr Raziallahu anhuma khadey huye aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko yahudiyon ki us baat ki khabar di, phir kehney lagey, kya hum haiz ki haalat mein unkey sath jima bhi na kar liya keren? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka chehra sakhti sey badal gaya yahan tak ke hamney samjha, aap un par naraz ho gaey hain, chunanche wo dono uth kar chaley gaey ke itney mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas doodh ka tohfa aa gaya to aap ney unkey peechey aadmi bheja aur unhein wapis bulwaya aur unhein doodh pilaya to wo samajh gaey ke aap hum par naraz nahin hain."
290,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey us shakhs key barey mein riwayat kartey hain jo apni biwi sey haiz ki haalat mein jima karta hai ke wo eik deenar ya nisf deenar sadqa kerey.
291,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke hum Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath nikley. hamara irada Haj hi ka tha. jab aap maqam sarf par they ke mujhey haiz shuru ho gaya. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) merey paas aaye to main ro rahi thi. aap ney farmaya : tumhein kya huwa? kya tumhein haiz shuru ho gaya hai? mainey kaha : haan. aap ney farmaya : ye chiz Allah Taala ney Adam ki betiyon par likh di hai, lihaza jo kuch haji keren, wohi tum bhi karo, sirf baitullah ka tawaf na karna. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (us Haj mein) apni biwiyon ki taraf sey gaey zibeh ki."
292,"Muhammad ( bin Ali al-Maaruf Imam Baaqar (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ) bayan kartey hain ke hum Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma key paas aaye aur un sey Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key Haj key mutalliq puchha to unhoney bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ( Haj key liye) nikley to zul-Qada key paanch din baqi they. hum bhi aap key sath nikley yahan tak ke aap Zul-Hulefa pahunchey to Asma bint Umes (Raziallahu anha) ney Muhammad bin abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko janm diya. unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko pegham bheja ke main kaisey karun ? aap ney farmaya : ghusl kar key langot baandh lo, phir labbaik kehna shuru kar do."
293,"Hazrat Umme-Qais bint Mohsin sey riwayat hai, unhoney Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey haiz key khoon key barey mein puchha jo kapdey ko lag jata hai. aap ney farmaya is ko kisi lakdi (ya haddi waghera ) sey khurch do, phir us ko pani aur beri key patton sey dho do."
294,"Hazrat Asma bint abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke eik aurat ney Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey haiz key khoon key barey mein puchha jo kapdey ko lag jaey to aap ney farmaya : usey khurch do, phir pani key sath ( nakhunon sey) mal do, phir dho kar namaz padh lo."
295,Hazrat Muawiya bin abu-Sufiyaan Raziallahu anhuma ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki pak biwi Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) sey puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) us kapdey mein namaz padhtey they jis mein jima kartey they? unhoney farmaya : haan! jab is mein koi aaludgi na dekhtey.
296,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key kapdey sey janabat ( mani ) ko dho deti thi, phir aap namaz key liye tashrif ley jatey jab ke pani key nishanat aap key kapdey mein nazar aatey they."
297,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke main Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key kapdey sey janabat ko khurch deti thi. aur eik baar farmaya : mani ko khurch deti thi.
298,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mujhey achi tarah yad hai ke main Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key kapdey sey mani ko ragad diya karti thi. us sey ziyada kuch nahin karti thi.
299,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke main Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key kapdey sey mani khurch diya karti thi.
300,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, wo farmati hain : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key kapdey mein mani dekhti to usey khurch deti."
301,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, wo farmati hain : mujhey achi tarah yad hai ke main Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key kapdey sey mani khurch diya karti thi."
302,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan farmati hain ke mujhey achi tarah yad hai ke main Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key kapdey mein mani dekhti to usey us sey khurch diya karti thi.
303,"Hazrat Umme-Qais bint Mohsin (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke main apney eik chhotey bachey ko jisney abhi khana shuru nahin kya tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas laee. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey apni god mein bitha liya. us ney aap key kapdey par peshab kar diya. aap ney pani mangwaya aur usey kapdey par chhidak diya aur usey dhoya nahin."
304,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik bacha laya gaya. us ney aap par peshab kar diya, chunanche aap ney pani mangwaya aur peshab par usey chhidak diya."
305,"Hazrat Abu-Samah Raziallahu anhu sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ladki key peshab ki wajeh sey kapda dhoya jaey aur ladkey key peshab ki wajeh sey pani chhidak diya jaey."
306,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Ukul qabiley key kuchh log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye aur kalima Islam padha phir wo kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum oonton waley log hain, kheti waley nahin aur unhoney Madiney ki aab aur huwa ko naa-muwaafiq paya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unkey liye oonton aur charwahey ka hukm diya aur unhein hukm diya ke un mein chaley jaaeyn aur unka doodh aur peshab piyen. phir jab wo tandurust ho gaey aur wo harra key eik kinarey mein reh rahey they. wo Islam laney key baad phir kafir ho gaey. unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key charwahey ko qatl kar diya aur aap key oont haank kar ley gaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye baat pahunchi to aap ney unkey peechhey talash karney waley bhejey. aakhir-kar unhein pakad kar laya gaya to musalmanon ney un ki aakhon mein garm salaiyan pherein aur unkey haath paaun kaat diye phir unhein usi zakhmi haalat mein harra mein chhod diya gaya yahan tak ke wo (tadaptey tadaptey) mar gaey."
307,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Uraina qabiley key kuchh badwi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye aur musalman ho gaey lekin unhoney Madiney ki aab aur huwa ko naa-muwaafiq paya yahan tak ke unkey rang zard ho gaey aur unkey pet badh gaey, chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein apni doodh wali oontniyon mein bhej diya aur un sey farmaya : unka doodh aur unka peshab piyen. yahan tak ke wo tandurust ho gaey to unhoney charwahey ko qatl kar diya aur oont haank kar ley gaey, chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein pakadney key liye aadmi bhejey. wo ( pakad kar) laye gaey to aap ney unkey haath paaun kaat diye aur un ki aakhon mein garm salaiyan pherein. Ameerul-momeneen Abdul-Malik ney Hazrat Anas Raziallahu anhu sey puchha jab ke wo unhein hadees bayan kar rahey they, ( un ki ye saza ) kufr ki wajeh sey thi ya gunah ki wajeh sey ? unhoney kaha : kufr ki wajeh sey. imaam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke hum nahin jantey ke Talha key ilawa kisi raawi ney is hadees mein an Yahya an Anas kaha ho. merey nazdik sahih sanad yun hai :( یحیی  بن سعید an سعید بن المسیب ) goya ye hadees mursal hai. (is mein Hazrat Anas ka zikr nahin hona chahiye.) ( wallah أعلم)"
308,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : (eik dafa) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Baitullah key paas namaz padh rahey they aur Quraish key sardar bhi bethey they. kisi ney eik oont zibeh kiya tha. un mein sey kisi ney kaha : kon hai jo ye gobar khoon samet utha kar laye, phir kuchh sabr karey yahan tak ke jab aap sajdey mein chehra rakhen to aap ki pusht par rakh dey? Hazrat Abdullah bayan kartey hain : chunanche eik bad-bakht utha gobar (waghera) utha kar laya  phir zara thehra. jab aap sajdey mein gir padey to usney wo ( sab kuchh ) aap ki pusht par rakh diya. Hazrat Fatima binte Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ittilaa ki gaee jab ke wo chhoti ladki thin. wo bhaagi bhaagi aayin aur ye gandagi aap ki pusht sey hata di. jab aap namaz sey farigh huye to teen dafa farmaya : aey Allah ! Quraish ko halak kar dey. ya Allah ! Abu-Jahal bin Hishaam, Sheeba bin Rabeea, Utba bin Rabeea aur Aqba bin Abi Mueet ko halak kar dey. yahan tak ke aap ney saat Qureshiyon key naam liye. Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke qism us zaat ki jisney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par Quran Majeed nazil farmaya ! mainey un sab ko Badr key din eik kunwen mein murda padey paaya."
309,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apni chadar ka eik kinara pakda is mein thookaa phir kapdey ko aapas mein mal diya."
310,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera Raziallahu anhu sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi aadmi namaz padh raha ho to wo apney aagey aur daeyn na thookey balke apney baain ya paaun key nichey thookey. warna Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney to Is tarah apney kapdey mein thook kar kapdey ko aapas mein mal liya tha."
311,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum eik safar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath nikley yahan tak ke jab hum bedaa ya zaatul-jaish maqam par pahunchey to mera haar gir gaya. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) us ko talash karney key liye thehar gaey. log bhi aap key sath thehar gaey jab ke na wahan pani tha aur na unkey paas pani tha. kuchh log Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaye aur (shikayatan) kaha : aap dekh nahin rahey hain ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney kya kiya hai? unhoney Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur logon ko thehra liya hai jab ke na to yahan pani hai aur na unkey paas pani hai. (ye baaten sun kar) Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aaye. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) meri raan par sar rakh kar so rahey they. wo aa kar kehney lagey : tum ney Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur logon ko rok rakha hai jab ke na yahan pani hai aur na unkey paas pani hai. mujhey Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney khub daantaa aur jo kehna chaha kaha aur wo merey pehlu mein kachokey maarney lagey. main harkat karney sey sirf is liye ruki rahi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) meri raan par they. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) soey rahey yahan tak ke baghair pani key subah ho gaee. to Allah Taala ney tayammum wali aayat utaar di. Hazrat Usaid bin Huzer (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : aey aale Abu-Bakar ! ye tumhaari koi pehli barkat nahin. Hazrat Aaisha ney kaha : phir hamney wo oont uthaya jis par main thi to haar uskey nichey sey mil gaya."
312,"Hazrat Abu Jaheem (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jamal kueyn ki taraf sey aaye. aap ko aagey sey eik aadmi mila aur us ney aap ko salam kaha. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey jawab na diya yahan tak ke aap eik deewar ki taraf gaey, chehrey aur haathon ka masah kiya, phir usey jawab diya."
313,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abzaa sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaya aur kehney laga : tehqiq main junbi (sambhog ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan) ho gaya aur pani na paa saka. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : to namaz na padh. Hazrat Ammaar bin Yaasir Raziallahu anhuma kehney lagey : aey Ameerul-momeneen ! kya aap ko yad nahin ke eik dafa main aur aap eik lashkar mein they. hum dono junbi (sambhog ya sawapandosh ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan) ho gaey to hamein pani na mila. aap ney to namaz na padhi lekin main achchhi tarah mitti mein lot-pot huwa aur namaz padh li phir hum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye aur aap sey is baat ka zikr kiya. aap ney farmaya : tujhey itna kafi tha. chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney dono haath zamin par maarey phir un mein phunk maari phir un dono key sath chehrey aur hatheliyon ka masah kiya. Salma ko shak hai, unhein yad nahin ke (masah) sirf hatheliyon par ya kohniyon tak kya tha. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : hum tumhein zimmey-daar banatey hain, is (riwayat) ka jis key tum zimmey daar baney ho."
314,"Hazrat Ammaar bin Yaasir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik dafa main oonton mein tha ke junbi (sambhog ya sawapandosh ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan) ho gaya. mujhey pani na mila to main mitti mein achchhi tarah lot pot huwa jaisey janwer karta hai, phir main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya to aap ko ye baat batai. aap ney farmaya : tujhey is (janabat (sambhog ya sawapandosh ke baad naapaaki ki haalat)) sey tayammum kafi tha."
315,"Hazrat Ammaar bin Yaasir Raziallahu Anhuma bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney zaatul-jaish mein padaaw dala jab ke aap key sath aap ki biwi mohtarma Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bhi thin. unka eik haar jo zifaar key nagoun ka tha, wo toot gaya. log us haar ki talash mein rok liye gaey yahan tak ke Fajr roshan ho gaee. logon key paas pani nahin tha. Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) par naraz huye aur farmaya : tum ney sab logon ko rok rakha hai jab ke unkey paas pani nahin hai, chunanche Allah Taala ney mitti key sath tayammum ki rukhsat (chhoot) nazil farma di. tamam musalman Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ke sath mein uthey aur zamin par apney haath maarey. phir unhoney apney haath uthaey aur koi mitti waghera nahin jhaadi so unhoney apney chehron aur bazuon ko kandhon tak aur apni hatheliyon sey baghlon tak haath pher liye."
316,"Hazrat Ammaar bin Yaasir Raziallahu Anhuma sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath mitti sey tayammum kiya. hamney apney chehron aur haathon ko kandhon tak mitti lagai."
317,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abzaa bayan kartey hain ke hum Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) key paas they. eik aadmi aap key paas aaya aur kehney laga : aey Ameerul-momeneen ! kabhi-kabhi hum eik eik, do do mahiney guzar detey hain aur pani nahin milta. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main to jab pani nahin paata, namaz nahin padhta yahan tak ke pani paa lun. Hazrat Ammaar bin Yaasir Raziallahu anhuma ney kaha : aey Ameerul-momeneen ! kya aap ko yad hai ke jab aap falan jagah mein they aur hum oont churaa rahey they to aap ko ilm hai ke hum junbi (sambhog ya sawapandosh ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan) ho gaey they? unhoney farmaya : haan ! chunanche main to mitti mein khub lithdaa tha, phir hum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye. aap hansey aur farmaya : tehqiq tujhey (itni hi) mitti kafi thi. ye keh kar aap ney zamin par hatheliyan maarin phir un mein phunka phir wo haath apney chehrey aur kuchh bazuon par mal liye. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : aey Ammaar ! Allah sey dar. Ammaar ney kaha : Ameerul-momeneen ! agar aap chahen to main ye waqiyaa zikr na karun. unhoney farmaya : nahin, hum tumhein zimmey-daar banatey hain, us chiz ka jis key tum zimmey-daar baney ho."
318,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abzaa sey riwayat hai ke kisi aadmi ney Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey tayammum key barey mein puchha to un ki samajh mein na aaya ke kya kahen? Hazrat Ammaar (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey, kya aap ko yad hai jab hum eik lashkar mein they to main junbi (sambhog ya sawapandosh ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan) ho gaya to main mitti mein lot pot huwa phir main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas gaya to aap ney farmaya : tumhein sirf is tarah kafi tha. aur Shoba ney apney haath apney ghutnon par maarey aur dono haathon mein phunka phir unhein chehrey aur hatheliyon par eik dafa mil liya."
319,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abzaa sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, unhoney kaha : eik aadmi junbi (sambhog ya sawapandosh ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan) ho gaya, chunanche wo Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaya aur kaha : tehqiq main junbi ho gaya aur pani na paa saka. unhoney farmaya : to namaz na padh. Hazrat Ammaar (Raziallahu anhu) ney un sey kaha : kya aap ko yad nahin ke hum eik lashkar mein they to hum junbi (sambhog ya sawapandosh ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan) ho gaey. aap ney to namaz na padhi lekin main achchhi tarah mitti mein luthdaa aur namaz padh li. phir main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur mainey ye baat aap sey zikr ki to aap ney farmaya : tujhey itna kafi tha. Shoba ( Hadees key raawi ) ney apni hatheli eik dafa zamin par maari phir is mein phunk maarii phir eik ko dusri sey mala phir unhein apney chehrey par mal liya. phir Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kuchh zikr kiya jo main nahin janta to Hazrat Ammaar (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : agar aap kahin to main ye hadees bayan na karun. Salma (raawi) ney Abu-Malik sey is sanad mein kuchh bayan kiya hai. aur Salma ney ye alfaz ziyada kahe hain ke Hazrat umr ney farmaya : hum tumhein is chiz ka zimmeydaar banatey hain jis key tum zimmey-daar baney ho."
320,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abzaa sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaya aur kehney laga : main junbi (sambhog ya sawapandosh ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan) ho gaya hun aur mujhey pani nahin milta. unhoney farmaya : to namaz na padh. Hazrat Ammaar (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : aey Ameerul-momeneen ! kya aap ko yad nahin ke jab main aur aap eik lashkar mein they, chunanche hum dono junbi (sambhog ya sawapandosh ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan) ho gaey aur hum pani na paa sakey. aap ney to namaz na padhi, lekin main achchhi tarah mitti mein lot pot huwa phir namaz padh li. jab hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye to mainey aap sey ye zikr kiya. aap ney farmaya : tujhey itna kafi tha. aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney haath zamin par maarey, phir un mein phunk maari aur unhein apney chehrey aur hatheliyon par mal liya. Salma raawi ko shak hai aur us ney kaha : main nahin janta ke (merey Shekh Zar ney) is mein kohniyon tak kaha ya hatheliyon tak. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : hum tumhein is chiz ka zimme-daar banatey hain jis key tum zimme-daar baney ho. Shoba ney kaha : (Salma raawi) kehtey they ke hatheliyon chehrey aur kohniyon ka masah kiya. (ye sun kar) Mansoor ney un sey kaha : (ghor karo) tum kya keh rahey ho? tehqiq kohniyon (par masah kerney) ka zikr tumharey siwa koi nahin karta. phir Salma ko shak huwa to usney kaha : main nahin janta ke us (Zar) ney kohniyon ka zikr kya ya nahin."
321,"Hazrat Shaqeeq bayan kartey hain ke main Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood aur Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari Raziallahu anhuma key paas betha tha. Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : kya aap ney suna nahin ke Hazrat Ammaar (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : mujhey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kisi kaam par bheja. main junbi (sambhog ya sawapandosh ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan) ho gaya aur main pani na paa saka to main mitti mein lot-pot huwa aur phir main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur mainey is baat ka zikr aap sey kiya. tab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tujhey itna kafi tha ke to aisey kar leta. phir aap ney apney haath zamin par eik dafa maarey, phir dono hatheliyon ko mala. phir unhein jhaada. phir baain haath ko daeyn aur daeyn ko baain par mala. is tarah apni hatheliyon aur chehrey par unhein pheraa. Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood ney kaha : kya tujhey ilm nahin ke Hazrat umr ney Hazrat Ammaar ki baat par qanaa'at na ki."
322,Hazrat Imran bin Husain Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ko alag bethey dekha jisney logon key sath namaz nahin padhi thi to aap ney farmaya : aey falan ! logon key sath namaz padhney sey tujhey kon si chiz rukaawat thi? to us ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main Junbi ho gaya hun aur pani nahin hai. aap ney farmaya : mitti istimal kar (tayammum kar ley) ye tujhey kafi hai.
323,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paak mitti musalman key liye zariyae-tahaarat (paakizgi) hai, chahey (chaahey) das saal pani na miley."
324,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Usaid bin Huzer aur kuchh doosrey logon ko Aaisha key haar ki talash mein bheja jisey wo apni manzil mein bhool gaee thin. namaz ka waqt ho gaya jab ke un (logon) ka wuzu nahin tha. wo pani na paa sakey to unhoney baghair wuzu key namaz padh li. phir unhoney is baat ka zikr Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey kiya to Allah Taala ney tayammum ki aayat utaar di. Hazrat Usaid bin Huzer (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey, Allah Taala aap ko jazaaey-khair ata farmaey. Allah ki qism ! jab bhi aap ko koi aisa maamla pesh aaya jisey aap pasand na karti hon to Allah Taala ney is mein aap key liye aur dusrey musalmanon key liye khair rakh di."
325,"Hazrat Taariq (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi junbi (sambhog ya sawapandosh ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan) ho gaya (aur usey pani na mila) to usney namaz na padhi. phir wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur aap ko ye baat batai to aap ney farmaya : tu ney theek kiya. eik aur aadmi junbi (sambhog ya sawapandosh ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan) ho gaya to usney tayammum kar key namaz padh li. wo aap key paas aaya to usey bhi aap ney wohi kaha jo doosrey ko kaha tha, yani tu ney theek kiya."
